(557, 'aparts/awLF80aQqyUg4Jfp6hooZmoFWjFTcfqc4XvfFAXv.webp', 'Connect with Experts and Advance Your Career', 'Digicrome supports and encourages students to connect with industry experts via webinars, Q and A sessions, and networking', '<p>Digicrome supports and encourages students to connect with industry experts via webinars, Q&amp;amp;A sessions, and networking events. This networking can further open work opportunities for you or help you gain knowledge you might otherwise remain unaware of.</p>', 1, 2, '2025-05-22 16:29:51', '2025-05-22 16:29:51'),
(558, 'aparts/XxynnXU4SZehH7B6efE1ONnkjzzB88juIwmU0R1W.webp', 'Learn from Industry-Leading Bankers', 'Each session is designed and delivered by seasoned professionals from top-tier investment banks who bring a wealth of practical knowledge and insights.', '<p>Each session is designed and delivered by seasoned professionals from top-tier investment banks who bring a wealth of practical knowledge and insights. You don’t just learn concepts — you get mentored by experts who’ve worked on IPOs, mergers, and billion-dollar deals. Their experience helps bridge the gap between classroom learning and real-world finance.</p>', 61, 2, '2025-06-07 22:21:29', '2025-06-07 22:21:29'),
(559, 'aparts/0q0BITTgA7VGSIJdq6liwHIyrs7F2zu1W9u0dmnz.webp', 'Real-Time Case Studies & Deal Analysis', 'Understanding investment banking is not just about theory. Our program integrates real-time case studies, live deal analysis', '<p>Understanding investment banking is not just about theory. Our program integrates real-time case studies, live deal analysis, and actual market scenarios so that you can apply your learning in practical situations. From analyzing mergers and acquisitions to decoding IPO launches, every concept is backed by relevant industry use-cases.</p>', 61, 2, '2025-06-07 22:22:36', '2025-06-07 22:22:36'),
(560, 'aparts/5TPa0V9wmiXwTr2xO7Sv0mQG6O859NKRaERmmek6.webp', 'In-Depth Financial Modeling & Valuation Training', 'Gain hands-on experience in building complex financial models just like analysts at global banks. Learn how to forecast cash flows', '<p>Gain hands-on experience in building complex financial models just like analysts at global banks. Learn how to forecast cash flows, value companies using DCF, comparable analysis, and LBO models. You’ll also master Excel tools and pitchbook creation — essential skills required to excel in investment banking roles.</p>', 61, 2, '2025-06-07 22:23:41', '2025-06-07 22:23:41'),
(561, 'aparts/NXJ8lR4hghbLKJpKIx0FZzdXsZbr9QOWwyGL86Or.webp', 'Weekend-Only Live Sessions for Working Professionals', 'We understand that your weekdays may be packed. That’s why our live classes are scheduled on weekends — with flexible options', '<p>We understand that your weekdays may be packed. That’s why our live classes are scheduled on weekends — with flexible options for morning or evening batches. This makes it easier for college students, working professionals, or career switchers to learn at their own pace without compromising on their routine.</p>', 61, 2, '2025-06-07 22:24:30', '2025-06-07 22:24:30'),
(562, 'aparts/bEt017iOk2zPHO7GVMiChHxmqv2PU938LkxTBcJy.webp', '1:1 Mentorship & Career Support', 'Get personalized guidance through dedicated mentors who help you at every stage of your journey. From resume-building and LinkedIn', '<p>Get personalized guidance through dedicated mentors who help you at every stage of your journey. From resume-building and LinkedIn optimization to mock interviews and job referrals — we ensure you’re not just course-ready but also career-ready. Our goal is to help you land your dream role in investment banking.</p>', 61, 2, '2025-06-07 22:25:08', '2025-06-07 22:25:08'),
(563, 'aparts/EDdPytyk1MkFtYUCAfFRH2dKTap8dtuzmwUpCNf6.webp', 'Hands-on Learning with Real Projects', 'Each idea is backed by real-globe practice', '<p>Each idea is backed by real-globe practice. From data cleaning to model building, you’ll work on real datasets, complete tiny-projects, and build a valise that justifies your proficient skills to employers.<br>&nbsp;</p>', 62, 2, '2025-06-16 16:42:07', '2025-06-16 16:42:07'),
(564, 'aparts/Z09e2z5a0QtnmWEb2lBa0cfhm5Zo9pmVIbXZJGJO.webp', 'Noida-Based Career Advantage', 'Being in Noida means you\'re learning in the heart of an IT and analytics hub.', '<p>Being in Noida means you\'re learning in the heart of an IT and analytics hub. Our course is created to align with local hiring flows, and we offer career guidance tailored to Noida’s job market<br>&nbsp;</p>', 62, 2, '2025-06-16 16:42:51', '2025-06-16 16:42:51'),
(565, 'aparts/AAn3ckvKmml9ZRWNncv9OLkoEi34Cff5IXNPRjBO.webp', 'Live Classes by Industry Experts', 'Our trainers are pros from the field who bring real-time happening and observations into the classroom.', '<p>Our trainers are pros from the field who bring real-time happening and observations into the classroom. With live classes, you get to ask questions, deal with doubts, and learn most practices straightforwardly from the professional.<br>&nbsp;</p>', 62, 2, '2025-06-16 16:43:32', '2025-06-16 16:43:32'),
(566, 'aparts/0tRA9UyEoUKTF8Z9bd7jguAhUPK7hfuAftkWmEvb.webp', 'Skill-Based, Job-Focused Curriculum', 'This course covers all top associations expect: Python, SQL, Power BI, Tableau, machine learning, and more', '<p>This course covers all top associations expect: Python, SQL, Power BI, Tableau, machine learning, and more. Every topic is taught with a job-oriented approach to assist you stand out in interviews.<br>&nbsp;</p>', 62, 2, '2025-06-16 16:44:06', '2025-06-16 16:44:06'),
(567, 'aparts/UWqOKnEZVXkikkFY2papzhGaWwnqSXrRmpx3rTlh.webp', 'Resume, Interview & Certification Support', 'We assist you prepare beyond just learning', '<p>We assist you prepare beyond just learning. Get certified, polish your resume with real projects, and practice interviews so you’re certain and ready when real opportunities come your manner.</p>', 62, 2, '2025-06-16 16:44:38', '2025-06-16 16:44:38'),
(568, 'aparts/QVAGTXAdQfi2peOLRv2jQa3P2GDMjeF7XDSsIpgK.webp', 'Learn in Gurgaon’s Tech-Driven Ecosystem', 'Gurgaon is a growing hub for tech and analytics.', '<p>Gurgaon is a growing hub for tech and analytics. Our course is made to match the talent require of top companies here, giving you direct access to local job opportunities and startup culture.<br>&nbsp;</p>', 63, 2, '2025-06-16 16:56:57', '2025-06-16 16:56:57'),
