(177, 61, 2, 'AML and Compliance Risk Management', '<p>Learn how to operate KYC/AML systems and file SAR reports. Learn how to identify suspicious transactions and become more regulatory compliant through interactive, scenario-based risk assessments.<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-07 16:35:39', '2025-06-07 16:35:39'),
(178, 61, 2, 'M&A Valuation and Deal Structuring', '<p>Get hands-on experience in DCF analysis of acquisition targets, as well as comparable analysis. Develop the skillset for structuring M&amp;A transactions, writing advisory reports, and practicing skills in real-time through a live project.<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-07 16:36:01', '2025-06-07 16:36:01'),
(179, 61, 2, 'IPO Advisory for Startups', '<p>Learn end-to-end IPO processes through scenario-based, hands-on practice—e.g., guiding a startup through valuation, capitalization, and investment planning. Hands-on, case-based exposure and experience on how IPOs function in real-world market situations.<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-07 16:36:25', '2025-06-07 16:36:25'),
(180, 61, 2, 'Ethical Decision Making', '<p>Witness a real-life situation where you\'re required to make an ethical decision. Apply professional standards in an advisory role and understand how such choices impact real client outcomes.</p>', '2025-06-07 16:36:43', '2025-06-07 16:36:43'),
(182, 75, 6, 'Design a Predictive Data Dashboard', '<p>Design a predictive data dashboard to visualize trends, forecast conclusions, and make more intelligent, data-driven resolutions with real-opportunity insights and analytics.</p>', '2025-07-11 11:12:12', '2025-07-11 11:12:12'),
(183, 75, 6, 'Gain Insights from Data with Tableau', '<p>Gain insights from data with Tableau by transforming inexperienced information into interactive, visual dashboards that disclose trends, patterns, and key profession brilliance.</p>', '2025-07-11 11:12:26', '2025-07-11 11:12:26'),
(184, 75, 6, 'Social Media-Based Sentiment Insights', '<p>Uncover social media-based belief insights to track common belief, monitor brand perception, and create informed decisions utilizing real-period emotional analysis and styles.</p>', '2025-07-11 11:12:43', '2025-07-11 11:12:43'),
(185, 75, 6, 'Build Your Own Smart AI Assistant', '<p>Build your own smart AI assistant to automate tasks, understand human language, and transfer personalized knowledge using leading, multi-model machine intelligence technology.</p>', '2025-07-11 11:12:57', '2025-07-11 11:12:57'),
(186, 77, 6, 'Create a Predictive Data Dashboard', '<p>Design smart dashboards to visualize flows, forecast outcomes, and make better, data-compelled decisions using original-time analytics and litigable insights.</p>', '2025-07-11 11:58:01', '2025-07-11 11:58:01'),
(187, 77, 6, 'Extract Insights with Tableau', '<p>Turn fresh data into interactive visualizations utilizing Tableau. Identify trends, reveal patterns, and highlight key business observations through powerful, user-friendly dashboards.</p>', '2025-07-11 11:58:15', '2025-07-11 11:58:15'),
(189, 77, 6, 'Develop a Smart AI Assistant', '<p>Build your own AI-stimulate assistant capable of understanding human language, automating tasks, and delivering personalized reactions using leading multimodal AI technologies.</p>', '2025-07-11 11:58:43', '2025-07-11 11:58:43'),
(190, 77, 3, 'Social Media Sentiment Analysis', '<p>Leverage sentiment analysis to record public opinion, monitor brand perception, and form informed determinations based on real-period emotional trends and public media data.</p>', '2025-07-11 12:30:15', '2025-07-11 12:30:15'),
(191, 78, 6, 'Design a Forecasting Dashboard', '<p>Create a knowledgeable dashboard that studies past data to predict future styles. It automatically detects key patterns and helps groups make better, timely outcomes.</p>', '2025-07-11 14:19:57', '2025-07-11 14:19:57'),
(192, 78, 6, 'Explore Data Using Tableau', '<p>Use Tableau to turn complex datasets into clear visuals. Build dashboards that reveal customer habits, sales performance, and trends that drive business action.</p>', '2025-07-11 14:20:13', '2025-07-11 14:20:13'),
(193, 78, 6, 'Run Sentiment Analysis on Social Media', '<p>Use NLP to understand how people feel online. Collect posts, process them, and classify emotions as positive, negative, or neutral to guide brand decisions.</p>', '2025-07-11 14:20:29', '2025-07-11 14:20:29'),
(194, 78, 6, 'Build a Multi-Modal AI Bot', '<p>Develop an AI structure that interacts with users through talk, text, and view. Enable features like face recognition, voice input, and document summarization.</p>', '2025-07-11 14:20:46', '2025-07-11 14:20:46');
