ks but we are not obligated to or so or to respond to you directly.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>We do not ensure that the information on this website is correct, we do not warrant its completeness or accuracy; nor do we promise to ensure that the website remains available or that the material on the website is kept up to date.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Refund Policy:<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you for buying our courses. We want to make sure that our users have a rewarding experience while they are discovering information, assessing, and purchasing our training courses, whether it may be for online or classroom training courses.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>As with any online purchase experience, below are the terms and conditions that govern the Refund Policy. When you buy a training course on the \'Digicrome\' website you agree to our Privacy Policy, Terms of Use, and the points below.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Digicrome Information Practices:<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Digicrome.com provides online training for many of the courses using this website. Our courses are designed to help project managers in professional certification exam preparation.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>\'Digicrome Academy\'. reserves the right to postpone/cancel an event or change the location of an event because of insufficient enrollments, instructor illness, or force majeure events (like floods, earthquakes, political instability, etc.).<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Cancellation &amp; Refunds: Online Training:<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Refund Policy:<br>&nbsp;</p><p>There is no refund available for purchasing online or self-paced courses.</p><p>Unlike physical goods, electronically distributed software and deliverables can be duplicated. Once a purchase has been made, it is unfortunately not possible for us to recall all copies/deliverables (such as downloaded files). Therefore, Digicromed does not accept refunds, returns, or exchanges.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>In case Digicrome cancels an event, 100% of course fees will be refunded to the delegate if the refund raise request is with