(2, 2, 'Advance Certification Program Business Analytics & Project Management', 'post-graduate-program-in-business-analytics-project-management', '4.5', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>Want to grow your career with real skills, you will be proud to have and even prouder to use? Apply to this <strong>Business Analytics and Project Management Course</strong>. This is an industry must-have.&nbsp;</p><p>It is carefully structured to give students and professionals the skills and experience required to stand out in this fast-moving business environment. This is the best Business Analytics course—whether you\'re new, working, or switching fields.</p><p><strong>Why Choose Digicrome\'s Advanced Certification Program?</strong></p><p>Looking through various <strong>Business Analytics Course</strong>, unsure which meets your educational needs and is worth the investment? Look no further, this is where you begin.</p><p>This <strong>Business Analytics Training</strong> is not an average course—it teaches job skills and tools such as Python, Tableau, Excel, Power BI, and more to make better decisions and right-value projects.</p><p>It brings together two strong skills—Business Analytics and Project Management—into one detailed business analytics and project management course. This course is created to help you understand data, make the right decisions, and more.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Business Analytics Course Syllabus</strong> has detailed 11 modules, ranging from data analysis techniques to project planning and execution + a 3-month internship, so you learn more than concepts.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>How will you benefit from this course?</strong></p><p>Complete this course and you will be equipped with the best skills to lead the industry.</p><ul><li><strong>Ability to make data-based decisions confidently:&nbsp;</strong>Students will be able to use data insights to make strategic business initiatives and improve performance.</li><li><strong>Manage projects efficiently:&nbsp;</strong>This cours