(6, 1, 'Post Graduate Program In Ui And Ux Design', 'post-graduate-program-in-ui-and-ux-design', '4.7', 'Catalyzing Your Career in UI/UX', '1', NULL, '<p>In the ever-evolving landscape of software applications, especially with the rise of the mobile platform, adherence to high standards of quality and operation has become imperative. UI/UX designers must navigate and embrace new norms in interface and experience design, making a UI/UX design certification course essential. This certification equips designers with the knowledge and skills needed to create seamless interfaces and exceptional user experiences, that align with contemporary industry standards.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Enroll in a UI/UX Design Certification Course?</strong></p>\r\n<p>With the stringent design principles prevalent in the mobile platform, modern UI/UX designers require up-to-date knowledge and skills. A UI/UX design certification course is essential to ensure designers can create interfaces and experiences that meet current industry standards across software applications.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Digicrome\'s PGP in UI/UX Design Course:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Digicrome\'s Post Graduate Program (PGP) in UI/UX Design has been meticulously designed to meet this crucial need. The course aims to empower UI/UX designers with comprehensive knowledge, practical skills, and hands-on experience. Delivered by seasoned professionals with extensive industry expertise, this course is tailored to the latest industry trends and techniques.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><strong>Comprehensive Curriculum:&nbsp;</strong>The program covers fundamental UI/UX processes, including wireframing, UI prototyping, UX writing, visual communication, interaction design, and coding.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Expert Faculty:</strong>&nbsp;Instructors are industry experts with in-depth knowledge and experience in UI/UX design. Their expertise is aligned with current industry trends, ensuring students receive the most relevant education.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Practical Learning:</strong>&nbsp;Emphasis is placed on practical experience, with projects encompassing informative website design, social media redesign, form design for the retail and banking sector, lead generation landing page design, and more.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Relevant Topics Covered:</strong>&nbsp;The curriculum spans various aspects of UX design, such as contextual inquiry, personas empathy map, stakeholder map, journey map, information architecture, content strategy planning, voice and tone assessment, SEO and accessibility, card sorting, taxonomies, mental models, wayfinding and navigation, and more.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Comprehensive Study Materials:</strong>&nbsp;Students have access to a variety of study materials, including videos, lectures, notes, assignments, surprise quizzes, and capstone projects, ensuring a well-rounded learning experience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Conclusion:</strong></p>\r\n<p>By enrolling in Digicrome\'s PGP in UI/UX Design, you embark on a transformative journey to gain in-depth knowledge and hands-on experience in creating user-friendly interfaces and exceptional user experiences.</p>\r\n<p>Elevate your career prospects in UI/UX design with this comprehensive and meticulously designed program, setting you on the path to success in the ever-evolving field of UI/UX design.</p>', NULL, 'Our Post Graduate Program in UI and UX Design will mold you into a well capable design professional, ready to establish excellent digital experiences, no matter your existing background. You can start here from core design principles to advanced user-centric plannings. This immersive UI/UX certification includes a inclusive internship in the curriculum. You\'ll gain hands-on experience with various tools and techniques, containing user research, wireframing, prototyping, visual design, and usability testing through practical projects and under the guidance of knowledgeable professionals.', 0, 1, NULL, '1', '06-Month Online Progr