(11, 1, 'DSAP (Data Science Analytics Professionals)', 'dsap-data-science-analytics-professionals', '4.5', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>Embrace the endless possibilities of data science with Digicrome\'s Data Analytics Certification program, designed to kickstart your journey into this rapidly evolving field. In today\'s technologically advanced world, data analytics has become indispensable, offering lucrative career opportunities across various industries. With our comprehensive certification course, you can delve into the realm of data science and unlock a world of possibilities.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://digicrome.com\"><strong>Why Choose Digicrome?</strong></a><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Industry Trends:</strong> Our curriculum is meticulously crafted to align with the latest industry trends, ensuring you stay ahead of the curve.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Holistic Learning Approach:</strong> We adopt a comprehensive approach to learning, covering every aspect of data science to groom candidates thoroughly.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Flexibility:</strong> Access classes anytime, anywhere with our convenient online platform, complete with automatic recording for future reference.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Practical Training: </strong>Focus on practical training empowers you with both theoretical knowledge and hands-on experience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dedicated Support:</strong> Our expert instructors are committed to addressing every query and clarifying concepts to ensure a clear understanding.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Eligibility Criteria:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Preferred: Graduates with basic knowledge of Python (beginner level).</li>\r\n<li>A strong understanding of data interpretation and visualization accelerates the learning process.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Course Highlights:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 120 hours of comprehensive training.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Complimentary E-Kit:</strong> Upon registration, receive a complimentary E-Kit containing sample papers, e-books, and system software requirements.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Live Virtual Classroom Training: </strong>Opt for our live virtual classroom training program and gain access to a free e-learning module.</li>\r\n<li><strong>24/7 Email Assistance:</strong> Benefit from round-the-clock email assistance and exam counselling to reinforce concepts covered in live sessions.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Recorded Sessions:</strong> Access recorded sessions anytime to revise and reinforce your learning.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Seize the opportunity to become a Data Science Analytics Professional with Digicrome\'s Data Analytics Certification. Enroll now and embark on a rewarding journey towards a successful career in data science.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '4 months', 105000.00, 4620.00, 1260.00, 0.00, 'DSAP (Data Science Analytics Professionals)', 'DSAP (Data Science Analytics Professionals)', 'DSAP (Data Science Analytics Professionals)', 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-25 12:52:55', 'https://www.digicromeacademy.com/assets/images/inner-img/course-thumb5.webp', NULL),
(12, 1, 'AI&ML (Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Professional)', 'aiandml-artificial-intelligence-and-machine-learning-professional', '4.8', 'AI That Changes Industries', '1', NULL, '<p>In the fast-paced realm of Information Technology (IT), Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Machine Learning (ML) have emerged as transformative forces, shaping industries and driving innovation. Digicrome\'s AIMLP Professional Certification Program offers a comprehensive deep learning experience, crafted to equip learners with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in AI and ML.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Course Overview:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Designed for aspiring Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Professionals, the AIMLP program aims to:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Provide a robust understanding of core AI and ML concepts.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Address major challenges in diverse work environments.</li>\r\n<li>Offer authentic, industry-relevant knowledge and practical insights.</li>\r\n<li>Foster global networking and collaboration opportunities.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Focus Areas:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Technical and theoretical aspects of AI and ML.</li>\r\n<li>Development of generalizable machine learning models.</li>\r\n<li>Exploration of reinforcement learning techniques.</li>\r\n<li>Practical application of tools like Keras and TensorFlow.</li>\r\n<li>Deployment of AI and ML algorithms across various industries.</li>\r\n<li>Hands-on experience with ML tools such as support vector machines, artificial neural networks, linear regression, and Python.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Skills Acquired:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The AIMLP certification course enhances learners\' proficiency and competency, preparing them for successful careers in AI and ML. Skills acquired include:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Heuristic programming and cognitive behaviour simulation.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Targeting roles such as ML Engineer, NLP Expert, AI Engineer, Data Analyst, and more.</li>\r\n<li>Practical application of AI and ML techniques in real-world scenarios.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Faculty and Experts:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Benefit from Digicrome\'s team of seasoned experts who deliver authentic knowledge through live interactive sessions, practical projects, and simulation exams. With 80 hours of comprehensive training, students gain valuable insights into the course curriculum and industry best practices.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Eligibility:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Candidates eligible for the AIMLP Professional Certification Program should have:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>A bachelor\'s degree in Computer Science, Statistics, Physics, or Electrical Engineering.</li>\r\n<li>Professionals in Analytics, Data Science, E-commerce, and Search Engine domains.</li>\r\n<li>Software professionals with relevant graduate degrees or certifications.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Job and Placement Opportunities:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Upon completing the program, graduates can pursue a wide range of career opportunities, including Big Data Engineer, ML Engineer, Data Scientist, Business Intelligence Developer, Research Scientist, AI Engineer, Product Manager, and more.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Seize Your Future in AI and ML:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Embrace the dynamic opportunities in AI and ML with <a href=\"../../upcoming-courses/post-graduate-program-in-data-science-and-artificial-intelligence\"><strong>Digicrome\'s AIMLP Professional Certification Program</strong></a>. Propel your career to new heights and become a trailblazer in the future of technology. Are you ready to shape the future? You can join us today.</p>', NULL, 'Our AI&ML (Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Professional) program will uplift you to the prominence of innovation, authorizing you to build intelligent systems and initiative data-driven solutions, regardless of your background. You will proceed from foundational AI concepts to advanced machine learning algorithms. This inclusive skilled certification involves extensive experiential projects and practical case studies. You will gain proficiency with various tools and techniques, containing Python, TensorFlow, Keras, deep learning, natural language processing, and computer vision, all under the supervision of experienced industry experts.', 0, 1, NULL, '1', '80 Hours', 55000.00, 2325.58, 633.34, 0.00, 'AI&ML (Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Professional)', 'AI&ML (Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Professional)', 'AI&ML (Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Professional)', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-25 12:53:56', 'courses/AhaRTcSaQyaXM1rivbgXdQMS4w6Dev5ZPAyEOEKc.webp', NULL),
(13, 1, 'Cybersecurity Job Oriented Certificate Program', 'cybersecurity-job-oriented-certificate-program', '4.5', 'Certified to Protect', '1', NULL, '<p>In today\'s digital landscape, cybersecurity stands as a paramount necessity in safeguarding sensitive information and thwarting cyber threats. At Digicrome, we offer an all-encompassing cybersecurity course program tailored to nurture aspiring Cyber Security Professionals and propel their careers to new heights. Our program equips individuals with the essential knowledge and skills vital for success in the dynamic realm of cybersecurity. Here\'s a glimpse into our comprehensive curriculum:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Introduction to Cybersecurity:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Gain insights into cybersecurity fundamentals, terminology, and its pivotal role in the digital age.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Network Security:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Master the art of securing network infrastructure and defending against diverse network-based attacks.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Systems Security:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Explore system architecture, operating system security, and strategies for mitigating system vulnerabilities.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Threat Intelligence:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Dive into intelligence analysis principles applied to cyberspace, enabling proactive threat assessment and risk mitigation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Governance, Risk Management, and Compliance:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Navigate governance frameworks, risk management processes, and compliance standards vital for ensuring information system security.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Logs &amp; Detection:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learn to analyze logs from various network devices to detect and respond effectively to security incidents.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Python for Cybersecurity:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Acquire foundational Python programming skills and leverage its power in automating tasks and analyzing security-related data.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Application Security and Penetration Testing:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Explore application vulnerabilities and penetration testing techniques to fortify applications against cyber threats.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cryptography and Encryption:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Delve into cryptography principles and applications, securing communication protocols and data encryption.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capstone Project:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Engage in a real-world cybersecurity project, applying acquired knowledge and skills to solve complex challenges and present findings professionally.</p>\r\n<p>Digicrome\'s cybersecurity course program offers a holistic training experience across various domains, empowering students for lucrative careers in cybersecurity. Join us to embark on a journey of knowledge, skill development, and career advancement in the ever-evolving field of cybersecurity.<br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Our Cybersecurity Job Oriented Certificate Program is planned to fast-track your career in the in-demand field of cyber defense, although your current technical background. This exhaustive program focuses on practical, job-ready skills, taking you from basic security ideas to advanced threat mitigation techniques. Through hands-on labs and real-globe projects, you\'ll gain mastery of various industry tools and methods, containing ethical hacking, network security, incident response, and vulnerability management, all under the supervision of trained experts. This program is specifically organized to equip you with the expertise employers seek, preparing you for immediate entry into valuable cybersecurity roles.', 0, 1, NULL, '1', '6 - Months', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'Cybersecurity Job-Oriented Certificate Program', 'Cybersecurity Job-Oriented Certificate Program', 'Cybersecurity Job-Oriented Certificate Program', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:16:34', 'courses/OJQ8BWG1E1jXpScbqBUAwUQ2kSB20rFK3lRW0rzP.webp', NULL),
(14, 1, 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 'certified-information-systems-security-professional-cissp', '4.5', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Join the elite league of cybersecurity experts with Digicrome\'s comprehensive CISSP Certification Training, accredited by the International Information Systems Security Certification Consortium (ISC)&sup2;. As pioneers in the field, we offer a robust curriculum designed to equip participants with the knowledge and skills required to excel in the CISSP exam and beyond. Dive deep into the fundamentals of information security and emerge as a sought-after professional capable of safeguarding organizations against evolving cyber threats.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Course Overview:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">The CISSP Certification is renowned as the gold standard in information security, recognized globally for its rigour and relevance. At Digicrome, our training program covers all eight domains of the CISSP Common Body of Knowledge (CBK), ensuring a comprehensive understanding of core security principles:</span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Security and Risk Management</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Asset Security</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Security Architecture and Engineering</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Communication and Network Security</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Identity and Access Management (IAM)</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Security Assessment and Testing</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Security Operations</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Software Development Security</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><strong>Intended Audience:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><strong>Ideal for professionals aspiring to excel in information security roles, including:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Chief Information Security Officers (CISO)</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">IT Directors</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">IT Security Consultants/Managers</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Security Architects/Auditors</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">IT Managers</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Security System Engineers</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Network Architects</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><strong>Course Essentials:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">To enrol in the CISSP Certification Training, participants must meet the following prerequisites:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Minimum of 5 years of full-time work experience in 2 or more of the 8 CISSP domains.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">A 4-year college degree or regional equivalent, or additional qualifications from the (ISC)&sup2; approved list, with a 1-year experience waiver.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><strong>Course Objectives:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Develop expertise in identifying and mitigating security breaches and threats.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Gain insights into enhancing security threads, telecommunications, and network security.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Learn to regulate and secure information processing resources across unified and distributed environments.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Master security assessment techniques and ethical hacking practices.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Understand security governance and risk management frameworks.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Build skills in software security concepts and practices.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><strong>Course Highlights:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">36-hour training delivered through self-paced e-learning, instructor-led live virtual classroom, and physical classroom sessions.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Experienced instructors share examination tips and tricks.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Access to crucial e-books, reference materials, and research papers.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Sample papers and mock tests for effective revision.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">1-day refund policy for unsatisfied participants.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Lifetime access to course materials and recorded sessions.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><strong>Course Delivery</strong>:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Led by industry experts with over 25 years of experience, our training emphasizes practical learning with real-time projects. Classes are conducted under constant trainer supervision, ensuring an optimal learning environment. Screen-sharing facilitates live virtual sessions, while a structured curriculum focuses on strengthening fundamental concepts.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">CISSP Examination Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Length: 3 hours (Computerized Adaptive Testing for English exams)</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Number of questions: 100 - 150 (Multiple choice and advanced innovative questions)</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Passing grade: 700 out of 1000 points</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Language availability: English, French, German, Brazilian Portuguese, Spanish, Japanese, Simplified Chinese, Korean</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Testing centres: (ISC)&sup2; Authorized PPC and PVTC Select Pearson VUE Centers</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><strong>Unlock Your Potential with CISSP Certification:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Gain practical and detailed knowledge of information security.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Access global industry opportunities.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Attract better job prospects.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Elevate your cybersecurity career with Digicrome\'s CISSP Certification Training and become a guardian of digital safety in today\'s interconnected world.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '40 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-07 12:30:54', 'courses/VeZ3Km8pWJvwYe8HeRVC49hc4HDZ3n35wsjPWtcv.webp', NULL),
(15, 1, 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional', 'aws-certified-solutions-architect-professional', '4.7', 'Advanced AWS Architecting', '1', NULL, '<p>Embark on a journey of technical mastery and professional advancement with the AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional exam. Designed to elevate your expertise in designing distributed applications and systems on the AWS platform, this certification is a testament to your ability to architect highly available, fault-tolerant, and scalable solutions. Here, we outline key insights and preparation essentials to guide you towards success in this prestigious certification.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Understanding the Exam:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional exam is tailored for individuals aspiring to perform the role of a Solutions Architect. It evaluates candidates on their ability to recognize and gather requirements, develop systems using new services, and evaluate architectural decisions. Key areas covered include:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Architecting High Availability and Business Continuity:</strong> Assessing stakeholder requirements, implementing disaster recovery strategies, and determining the use of multi-availability Zones vs. multi-region architectures.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cost Optimization:</strong> Making architectural decisions to minimize infrastructure costs, comparing cost implications of different architectures, and optimizing AWS account and billing set-up options.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Deployment Management:</strong> Managing the lifecycle of applications on AWS, selecting appropriate deployment mechanisms, and positioning environments for development, testing, and staging.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Network Design:</strong> Designing and implementing networking features, and applying connectivity features of AWS.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Data Storage:</strong> Making architectural trade-off decisions involving storage options, selecting the most appropriate data storage architecture, and determining replication methodologies.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Security: </strong>Designing information security management systems, implementing security controls, and protecting data at rest and in transit.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Scalability &amp; Elasticity: </strong>Designing loosely coupled systems, implementing front-end, middle-tier, and data storage scaling architectures, and evaluating trade-offs between vertical and horizontal scaling.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cloud Migration &amp; Hybrid Architecture: </strong>Planning and executing application migrations, and designing hybrid cloud architectures.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Exam Eligibility:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>To be eligible for the exam, candidates must have:</li>\r\n<li>Achieved AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate certification.</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 years of experience in designing and deploying cloud architecture on AWS.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to evaluate cloud application requirements and provide architectural recommendations.</li>\r\n<li>Proficiency in providing best practices guidance on architectural design across multiple applications or projects.<br><br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Examination Details:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> AWS Certified Solutions Architect &ndash; Associate<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Format:</strong> Multiple-choice and multiple-answer questions</p>\r\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 170 minutes</p>\r\n<p><strong>Languages: </strong>English and Japanese</p>\r\n<p><strong>Practice Exam Fee:</strong> USD 40</p>\r\n<p><strong>Exam Registration Fee:</strong> USD 300</p>\r\n<p><strong>Preparation Essentials:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prepare for success with the following resources:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Architecting on AWS:</strong> Deep dive into advanced concepts of architecting on AWS.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>AWS Cloud Computing White Papers:</strong> Explore topics such as security processes, storage options, fault-tolerant applications, compliance, and more.</p>\r\n<p><strong>AWS Architecture Center: </strong>Utilize the wealth of resources available for architecting AWS cloud solutions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advanced Architecting on AWS: </strong>Consider enrolling in advanced training courses to enhance your knowledge and skills.</p>\r\n<p>Mastering AWS as an AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional opens doors to limitless opportunities in cloud architecture and design. Start your journey today and redefine your career with AWS expertise.</p>', NULL, 'The AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional validates your advanced expertise in designing well adaptable, fault-tolerant, cost-adept, and secure cloud architectures on Amazon Web Services. This professional-level certification goes beyond basic knowledge, challenging your strength to make complex architectural decisions in diverse scenarios. You\'ll get mastery of various AWS services, progressive design patterns, and operational best practices, preparing you for senior-level roles in cloud architecture. This certification is a testament to your strength to lead and implement complex cloud solutions, under the direction of experienced industry experts and through practical, hands-on application.', 0, 1, NULL, '1', '30 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional', 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional', 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Professional', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:24:16', 'courses/Q9YUE2wZlQAZpnbrzrlnacKWjKPU5LL57frTg9LE.webp', NULL),
(16, 1, 'Scrum Product Owner Professional By SCRUMVersity', 'scrum-product-owner-professional-by-scrumversity', '4.6', 'Train with the Best', '1', NULL, '<p><strong>Scrum Product Owner Certification: A Pathway to Agile Excellence</strong></p>\r\n<p>Scrum Product Owner Professionals (SPOPs) are individuals equipped with the knowledge, practices, and principles of Scrum methodology, enabling them to effectively fulfil the role of Product Owner within a Scrum team. Positioned closest to the business side of the project, SPOPs are entrusted with the responsibility of delivering the product and ensuring stakeholder satisfaction.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Maintain product development momentum.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Communicate and prioritize requirements.</li>\r\n<li>Uphold team collaboration and understanding of project objectives.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits of Scrum Product Owner Certification:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Gain proficiency in new Scrum methodologies.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Showcase existing and newly acquired skills.</li>\r\n<li>Enhance product management expertise.</li>\r\n<li>Stay abreast of industry trends and advancements.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Exam Format:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Multiple choice questions.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>60 questions per exam.</li>\r\n<li>No negative marking.</li>\r\n<li>90 minutes duration.</li>\r\n<li>Proctored online exam.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Audience Profile:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Professional Scrum Product Owner course is ideal for professionals involved in software development within the Scrum framework, particularly those focused on business and product management aspects. It is tailored for individuals assuming the role of Scrum Product Owner.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To embark on the journey towards becoming a Scrum Product Owner Professional (SPOP), it is essential to familiarize yourself wi