se with a duration of 40 hours</li>\r\n<li>Live classes conducted via video conferencing</li>\r\n<li>Dedicated group discussions to enhance learning</li>\r\n<li>Comprehensive provision of study materials and lecture notes</li>\r\n<li>Practical and theoretical projects to reinforce learning</li>\r\n<li>Multiple test series and simulation papers for assessment</li>\r\n<li>Course completion certificate and regular job assistance</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Intermediate Course - B1:</strong></p>\r\n<p>In the first part of the Intermediate level, learners focus on expanding their vocabulary, enhancing linguistic skills, and engaging in social communication. They delve into current events, personal traits, and professional expertise, honing their ability to discuss procedures, frequencies, and environmental issues.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Intermediate Course - B2:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The second part prepares learners to navigate real-world scenarios confidently. They discuss advertisements, consumer trends, and financial matters, utilizing complex grammatical structures and descriptive language. Through discussions on entertainment and personal emotions, learners refine their expressive abilities in English.</p>\r\n<p>Join Digicrome\'s Intermediate English Course today and embark on a transformative journey towards linguistic proficiency and personal growth.<br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '40 Hours Program', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'English Language Training(B1&B2)', 'English Language Training(B1&B2)', 'English Language Training(B1&B2)', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-25 12:59:32', 'courses/yQ1pefPOP4ZT2i7PNZEmHf7KZTBI1PrkFu3M2zzZ.webp', NULL),
(31, 1, 'PMPÂ® Certification Training', 'pmpa-certification-training', '4.7', 'Keep Working While You Certify', '1', NULL, '<p>The Project Management Professional (PMP) certification is widely recognized as the gold standard in project management. Offered by the prestigious Project Management Institute (PMI), this certification is a testament to a project manager\'s expertise and proficiency. At Digicrome, we offer comprehensive PMP certification training programs designed to prepare aspiring professionals for success in the field of project management.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Pursue PMP Certification?</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Global Recognition:</strong> The PMP certification is globally recognized and highly respected by employers across industries. It demonstrates your commitment to excellence and your ability to lead and manage projects effectively on a global scale.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Career Advancement:</strong> Achieving PMP certification opens up new career opportunities and positions you for advancement in your current role. Many organizations prefer or require PMP-certified project managers for leadership positions.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Enhanced Skills: </strong>The PMP certification program enhances your skills and knowledge in project management, equipping you with the latest tools, techniques, and best practices endorsed by PMI.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Increased Marketability:</strong> PMP certification increases your marketability and credibility in the job market. It validates your expertise and distinguishes you as a qualified and capable project manager.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Our Approach to PMP Certification Training:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Comprehensive Curriculum: </strong>Our PMP certification training program is designed to cover all the key areas of project management as outlined in the Project Management Body of Knowledge (PMBOK) guide. We provide in-depth instruction on project management processes, methodologies, and best practices.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Experienced Instructors:</strong> Our instructors are highly experienced industry professionals with over 25 years of work experience in project management. They bring real-world expertise and insights to the training, ensuring that participants receive practical and relevant instruction.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Structured Learning Paradigm:</strong> Our training follows a structured paradigm that progresses from foundational concepts to intermediate and advanced levels. We focus on building a strong foundation of knowledge and skills that will remain relevant long after the training period ends.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Interactive Learning: </strong>We believe in interactive learning experiences that engage participants and facilitate knowledge retention. Our training sessions include real case studies, events, and discussions to provide a comprehensive understanding of project management complexities.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Course Highlights:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>36 hours of training sessions led by certified professionals<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>54 hours of e-learning sessions with illustrated ebooks</li>\r\n<li>Real case studies and simulations to simulate real-world scenarios</li>\r\n<li>Full-length simulation tests with 200 questions</li>\r\n<li>Value guidelines, tips, and techniques for exam success</li>\r\n<li>Access to essential reading material, updates, and reference books</li>\r\n<li>Downloadable courseware and handouts for easy reference</li>\r\n<li>1-day money-back guarantee for participant satisfaction</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Course Delivery:</strong></p>\r\n<p>We offer PMP certification training through three modes: self-paced e-learning, instructor-led live online virtual classroom training, and physical classroom training. Our experienced instructors use live video streaming technologies, interactive sessions, online chats, and screen-sharing facilities to deliver engaging and effective training.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits of PMP Certification Training at Digicrome:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Gain essential knowledge, skills, and techniques for PMP certification success<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Understand project management concepts, theories, formulas, methods, and terminology</li>\r\n<li>Learn advanced strategies for answering exam questions quickly and accurately</li>\r\n<li>Access additional practice questions and resources to enhance exam readiness</li>\r\n<li>Achieve high scores on the PMP exam and earn international recognition</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Embark on your journey to PMP certification with Digicrome and unlock new opportunities for career advancement and professional growth.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '36 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'Online PMPA Certification – Learn Project Management Skills', 'PMPÂ® Certification Training', 'Join PMPA Certification Training to learn project management essentials and get ready for the PMI exam with expert guidance and real-world scenarios.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:18:11', 'courses/vSCNeXuRWozyWx66ikLxk7ySkQEDp1KujnjJdW7m.webp', NULL);
