sh Graduates in Bachelors or Master&acirc;&euro;&trade;s Degree Our Faculty and Experts At Digicrome, the world-class faculty is staunch in teaching the students what is right and what is in trend in the industry market. They train and prepare the next generation of professionals towards creating a new sky and land for themselves, where they can map their technological and scientific victory. What Important skills will you learn with this Data science course? Have an in-depth understanding of data structure and data manipulation Understand and use linear and non-linear regression models and classification techniques for data analysis Learn in-depth knowledge of Data Wrangling Obtain an in-depth understanding of supervised and unsupervised learning models such as linear regression, logistic regression, clustering, and dimensionality reduction. Gain expertise in mathematical computing using the NumPy Master the concepts of recommendation engine and time series modeling and gain practical mastery over principles, algorithms, and applications of machine learning Learn to analyze data using Tableau and become proficient in building interactive dashboards Understand the concept of Machine Learning Get an in-depth understanding of Data Visualization Is data science a good career option? Yes, Data Science is one of the most highly paid jobs. According to Glassdoor, Data scientists make an average of $116,100 per year. This makes Data Science extensive career option. What are In-Demand Data Science Careers? Here are some of the leading data science careers you can fetch after completion of this course. Data Scientist Machine Learning Engineer Machine Learning Developer Applications Architect Enterprise Architect Data Architect Infrastructure Architect Data Engineer Business Intelligence (BI) Developer Statistician Data Analyst</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '120 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'Data Science Professional Certification', 'Data Science Professional