(33, 1, 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 'certified-information-systems-security-professional-cissp', 'a33', NULL, 'Yes', NULL, '<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">The Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP) certification stands as the pinnacle of achievement in the realm of information security. Administered by the renowned International Information Systems Security Certification Consortium (ISC2), CISSP certification validates professionals\' expertise across various domains of information security. At Digicrome, we take pride in offering a comprehensive CISSP certification training program meticulously crafted to equip participants with the requisite knowledge and skills to thrive in the dynamic field of information security.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Unique Features of Our CISSP Certification Training:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Rigorous Curriculum:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Our CISSP certification training comprehensively covers all eight domains of the CISSP Common Body of Knowledge (CBK), ensuring participants develop a profound understanding of essential concepts crucial for securing modern business environments. From Security and Risk Management to Security Engineering, participants delve deep into each domain under the guidance of seasoned industry professionals.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Experienced Instructors:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Led by seasoned industry veterans with over 25 years of experience in information security, our instructors employ a blend of heuristic training methodologies tailored to meet participants\' diverse learning needs. Their wealth of practical experience enriches the learning journey, offering insights and perspectives garnered from real-world scenarios.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Flexible Delivery Modes:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Participants can opt for their preferred mode of learning from our diverse range of delivery options, including self-paced e-learning, instructor-led live virtual classroom training, and physical classroom sessions. Led by experts from esteemed organizations like Google, Microsoft, and IBM, our boot camp sessions ensure a rich learning experience regardless of the chosen format.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Hands-on Learning:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Our training prioritizes hands-on learning, providing participants with practical skills essential for tackling real-world security challenges. Through live video streaming technologies, interactive sessions, and online chats, participants engage actively in the learning process, reinforcing their understanding of key concepts.<br><br></span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>CISSP Examination Information:<br></b><br>The CISSP exam is available in two formats: Computerized Adaptive Testing (CAT) and Linear Examination. The exam consists of multiple-choice and advanced innovative questions, and candidates must achieve a passing grade of 700 out of 1000 points.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Benefits of CISSP Certification:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Some of the benefits of achieving CISSP certification include gaining practical and detailed knowledge of information security, accessing global industry systems, and attracting better job opportunities.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Comprehensive Support:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">We offer participants access to a wealth of resources, including e-books, reference materials, recent research papers, sample papers, and mock tests. These resources facilitate effective revision and exam preparation, empowering participants to excel in their CISSP certification journey.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Lifetime Access:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Upon completion of the training, participants receive lifetime access to all course materials and recorded sessions, enabling continuous learning and skill enhancement at their convenience.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><b style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Conclusion:</b><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">In conclusion, Digicrome\'s CISSP certification training program is designed to empower professionals with the knowledge, skills, and credentials needed to excel in the competitive landscape of information security. With practical insights, global recognition, and enhanced job prospects, CISSP certification opens doors to unparalleled career opportunities in the cybersecurity domain. Join us at Digicrome and embark on a transformative journey towards professional excellence in information security.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '40 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-10 15:16:32', 'https://www.digicromeacademy.com/assets/images/inner-img/course-thumb5.webp', '2025-06-10 15:16:32'),
(34, 1, 'CISA Certification Training', 'cisa-certification-training', '4.8', 'Proven Training for CISA Success', '1', NULL, '<h2>Course Description</h2>\r\n<p>The CISA exam is offered by the Information Systems Audit and Control Association (ISACA). The exam has become the industry customary for IT auditing, control, and security. CISA Certification Training course is associated with the latest 2019 version of the CISA exam and makes certain that you top the exam in your primary attempt. This course helps the candidates to obtain the latest, relevant and brief knowledge through practical practice exams to prepare for the CISA certification exam. The CISA assignment is a comprehensive known affirmation for Information Systems review control, approval, and security experts. This CISA course exhibits your review involvement, skills, learning, and further supports your capacities to survey liabilities, cover consistency and groundwork controls in the project. You will similarly pick up ability in the procurement, advancement, testing, and usage of data structures; understand the rules and best practices of securing them. The CISA Certification Training course will advance your knowledge of IS audit and also support you know how to safeguard information systems. Why CISA CISA certification enables you to stand out from the frontlines to the meeting room. Makes you highly qualified and well-practiced professionals Makes you proficient in technology controls CISA qualified demonstrates competence in five domains Makes you upkeep current development for effective on-the-job performance Audience Profile CISA Certification Training program is essential for professionals, like: Professionals, Security Consultants/Managers dealing in Information Security Management IT Directors/Managers accountable for Information Security Security Auditors/Architects Security System Engineers Chief Information Security Officers Network Architects ISMS Members Eligibility Standard At least 5 years of professional data systems auditing, control or security work experience is obligatory for certification. Waivers of such experience, to a maximum of 3 years, might be acquired as follow: A maximum of 1 year of information systems understanding or 1 year of non-IS auditing experience can be relieved for 1 year of experience. A 2 or 4-year degree can be relieved for 1 or 2 years, respectively, of experience. A master&acirc;&euro;&trade;s degree in information security or information technology from a recognized college can be relieved for 1 year of experience. Learning Outcome Upon the completion of the CISA Certification Training program, the trainees would be able to: Recognize and evaluate vulnerabilities and report on the agreement and institutional controls Know IS audit and assurance plans, standards, and best practices Know and acquire how to oversee and control initiative IT environments Know the attainment, development, testing, and execution of information systems Determine working understanding of the five domains of CISA, as set by ISACA Get the appropriate understanding and skills needed to clear the CISA Certification exam by ISACA. Career Scopes The successful achievement of certification will lead contenders for the following job roles: Information security manager/consultant Technical consultant Operational risk manager Analysts Compliance managers Project manager Cloud security IT auditor Course Highlights The CISA Certification Training course is led by experienced and certified faculties Students are provided course materials Instructors are highly experienced Sample tests for actual exam preparation Exam Layout Exam Type: Online Duration: 240 mins. No.of Questions: 150 Passing Percentage: 60%</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '36 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'CISA Certification Training – Become a Certified Auditor', 'CISA Certification Training', 'Enroll in CISA Certification Training to master IT auditing, control, and security. Get expert guidance, exam prep, and boost your career in cybersecurity.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:16:13', 'courses/2Mr8SSnm6suRcPCWsfG2kNRsAdavO9MsP2ZfHFPp.webp', NULL),
(35, 1, 'CISM Certification Training', 'cism-certification-training', '4.7', 'Get CISM Certified', '1', NULL, '<p>Digicrome offers the Certified Information Security Manager (CISM) Certification Training, an essential program designed for advanced professionals across diverse industries. Administered by ISACA, the CISM certification exam has emerged as the industry standard for progression in information security. This certification targets experts involved in IT security management and governance, making it indispensable for information security professionals overseeing, planning, and evaluating enterprise information security practices. The CISM Certification Training program at Digicrome provides participants with comprehensive knowledge and skills in IT security systems. This management-oriented certification fosters global security practices and addresses the rising demand for experienced information security management professionals, establishing the CISM certification as the benchmark for success in this field.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Audience Profile:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The CISM Certification Training program at Digicrome is ideal for:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Information Security Managers<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Aspiring Information Security Managers</li>\r\n<li>IS/IT Consultants</li>\r\n<li>Security Auditors and Architects</li>\r\n<li>Security System Engineers</li>\r\n<li>Chief Information Security Officers (CISOs)</li>\r\n<li>Risk Officers</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Eligibility Standard:</strong></p>\r\n<p>To enrol in the CISM Certification Training program at Digicrome, candidates must meet the following eligibility criteria:<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Minimum of five years of experience in the field of information security<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Work experience obtained within ten years before applying for certification or within five years of passing the exam</li>\r\n<li>At least three of the five years of work experience must involve serving as an information security leader.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Course Objective:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>The CISM Certification Training program at Digicrome aims to equip participants with the following skills:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Aligning information security strategies with organizational objectives<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Developing an information security governance framework</li>\r\n<li>Managing IT risks to an organizationally acceptable level</li>\r\n<li>Creating an information security program that identifies, manages, and protects organizational assets</li>\r\n<li>Developing and implementing incident response capabilities to mitigate the impact of security events on the business</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Learning Outcome:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Upon completing the CISM Certification Training program at Digicrome, participants will master the following:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Information Security Governance<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Information Security Incident Management</li>\r\n<li>Security Architecture Design</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of ISACA domains</li>\r\n<li>Information Security Programs</li>\r\n<li>Enterprise IT frameworks</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits of CISM Certification:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Direct validation of qualifications<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Enhanced confidence among employers, colleagues, and clients</li>\r\n<li>Increased marketing and income potential</li>\r\n<li>Demonstration of the ability to stay ahead of evolving risks</li>\r\n<li>Global recognition as one of the best in the field</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Career Scopes:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Individuals with the CISM credential can pursue various high-profile job roles, including:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Information Security Manager<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Chief Information Officer</li>\r\n<li>Information Risk Compliance Specialist</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Course Highlights:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Instructor-led training by experienced CISM-certified professionals<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Practice tests to familiarize participants with the exam format and difficulty level</li>\r\n<li>Tailored training to maximize success in the CISM exam</li>\r\n<li>24/7 assistance and support for candidates to optimize their performance</li>\r\n</ol>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '32 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'CISM Certification Training – Advance Your Cybersecurity Career', 'CISM Certification Training', 'Get CISM-certified with comprehensive training. Learn security management, risk handling, and compliance from industry experts to boost your leadership role.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-12 09:56:23', 'courses/RCuPBRsGAjjsglZM10KXXReO3xmzeKDpWrfB4UPL.webp', NULL),
(36, 1, 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate', 'aws-certified-solutions-architect-associate', '4.7', 'Your Foundation for AWS Excellence', '1', NULL, '<p>To become an AWS Certified Solutions Architect through Digicrome, you can enrol in our specialized training program designed to prepare you for success in the certification exam. <strong>Here\'s how our course can help you achieve your goals:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Comprehensive Training Program:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Our AWS Certified Solutions Architect training program covers all the necessary topics and domains required to pass the certification exam.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>You will learn about designing highly available, cost-efficient, fault-tolerant, and scalable systems on the AWS platform.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Experienced Instructors:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Our instructors are industry experts with extensive experience in AWS solutions architecture.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>They will guide you through the course material and provide valuable insights based on real-world scenarios.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Flexible Learning Options:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>We offer flexible learning options, including self-paced e-learning, instructor-led live virtual classroom training, and physical classroom training.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>You can choose the mode of learning that best fits your schedule and learning preferences.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Hands-on Experience:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Our training emphasizes practical, hands-on learning to ensure you develop the skills needed to succeed in real-world scenarios.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>You will have access to AWS resources and labs to practice your skills and reinforce your understanding of key concepts.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Comprehensive Support:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Throughout the training program, you will receive comprehensive support, including access to study materials, practice exams, and expert guidance.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Our instructors will be available to answer your questions and provide assistance whenever needed.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Exam Preparation:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Our course is specifically designed to prepare you for the AWS Certified Solutions Architect exam.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>You will receive guidance on exam preparation strategies, access to practice exams, and tips for maximizing your performance on exam day.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Proven Track Record:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Our training program has a proven track record of success, with many students achieving their certification goals and advancing their careers in cloud computing.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>By enrolling in our AWS Certified Solutions Architect training program at Digicrome, you will receive the knowledge, skills, and support you need to become certified and excel in the field of cloud computing.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>To become an AWS Certified Solutions Architect, you need to meet certain requirements and possess specific knowledge and skills.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Here\'s a summary of the steps and qualifications needed:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>1. Eligibility Criteria:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Hands-on experience with AWS services in computer, networking, storage, and database.</li>\r\n<li>Professional experience in architecting large-scale distributed systems.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of elasticity and scalability concepts.</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with AWS global infrastructure and network technologies.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of AWS security features, deployment, and management services.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of AWS client interfaces and deployment best practices.</li>\r\n<li>General IT knowledge including multi-tier architectures, relational databases, NoSQL, message queuing, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>2. Other Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Completion of Architecting on AWS training or equivalent knowledge.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Proficiency in at least one high-level programming language.</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with AWS Cloud Computing White Papers, Security Processes, Risk &amp; Compliance, Storage Options, and Best Practices.</li>\r\n<li>Experience with hybrid systems integrating on-premises and AWS components.</li>\r\n<li>Utilization of the AWS Architecture Center website for learning.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>3. Eligibility for Exam:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minimum 1 year of experience in designing fault-tolerant, scalable distributed systems on AWS.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Deep knowledge of at least one high-level programming language.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to define requirements for AWS-based applications and implement best practices for secure and reliable applications.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>4. Exam Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The exam consists of multiple-choice and multiple-answer questions.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Duration: 80 minutes.</li>\r\n<li>Available in multiple languages.</li>\r\n<li>Registration fee: USD 150.</li>\r\n<li>Practice exam registration: USD 20.</li>\r\n<li>Domains covered: Designing highly available, cost-efficient, fault-tolerant, scalable systems; Implementation/Deployment; Data Security; Troubleshooting.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>5. Exam Preparation:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Study AWS documentation, white papers, and best practices.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Enroll in AWS training courses or use online resources.</li>\r\n<li>Take practice exams to familiarize yourself with the format and content.</li>\r\n<li>Review sample questions and understand the rationale behind correct answers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>By meeting the eligibility criteria, preparing diligently, and passing the certification exam, you can become an AWS Certified Solutions Architect and demonstrate your expertise in designing and implementing scalable, fault-tolerant systems on the AWS platform.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '32 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate', 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate', 'AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:21:04', 'courses/3pUz7zTrvvgn1sR04EQfBlRPVu6srnJ3024GBjz3.webp', NULL),
(37, 1, 'AWS Certified Developer - Associate', 'aws-certified-developer-associate', '4.9', 'Power Up with AWS.', '1', NULL, '<p>Achieving the AWS Certified Developer Associate certification signifies a deep understanding and proficiency in designing, developing, and deploying cloud-based solutions using Amazon Web Services (AWS). This certification exam is tailored for individuals aspiring to excel in developer roles within the AWS ecosystem.</p>\r\n<p>Mastering AWS Development requires a multifaceted approach, encompassing both theoretical knowledge and hands-on experience. This professional certification validates not only the ability to select the right AWS services for specific applications but also the aptitude to leverage AWS SDKs effectively to optimize performance and ensure robust security measures.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To succeed in the AWS Certified Developer Associate exam, candidates must possess a solid foundation in IT concepts, including stateless and loosely coupled distributed applications, RESTful API interfaces, relational and non-relational databases, and messaging queuing services.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Preparation for this exam involves comprehensive training through resources such as the \"Developing on AWS\" course, an in-depth understanding of at least one high-level programming language, a thorough review of AWS Cloud Computing White Papers, and meticulous study of AWS documentation.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The exam blueprint outlines four domains, each carrying a specific weightage:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>AWS Fundamentals (10%): </strong>Candidates must demonstrate proficiency in identifying and recognizing cloud architecture considerations, understanding fundamental components, and making effective design decisions. This includes knowledge of design and cloud services, database concepts, and architectural trade-off decisions.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Designing and Developing (40%):</strong> This domain assesses the ability to identify appropriate techniques for coding cloud solutions, including configuring Amazon Machine Images (AMIs) and programming with AWS APIs.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Deployment and Security (30%):</strong> Candidates are evaluated on their understanding and implementation of highly secure processes for optimal cloud usage and maintenance. This involves demonstrating the ability to apply the right architecture for development, testing, and staging environments, as well as proficiency in cloud security best practices, AWS platform compliance, and security services.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Debugging (20%): </strong>This domain evaluates candidates\' troubleshooting skills and knowledge of best practices in debugging, ensuring they can effectively address and resolve issues within AWS environments.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Eligibility for this certification requires candidates to have at least one year of hands-on experience designing and maintaining AWS-based applications, deep knowledge of at least one high-level programming language, and proficiency in designing and developing cloud-based solutions using AWS services.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>By mastering AWS development and obtaining the Certified Developer Associate certification, professionals can unlock new opportunities in the rapidly growing field of cloud computing and establish themselves as skilled AWS developers.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cost: USD 150 for exam registration, and USD 20 for practice exam registration.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '28 Hours', 70000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'AWS Certified Developer - Associate', 'AWS Certified Developer - Associate', 'AWS Certified Developer - Associate', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-25 13:00:47', 'courses/qZaeR48tIfqFvKcIqKmFgN0QpLydgLbYhRsQPlQR.webp', NULL),
(38, 1, 'AWS Certified SysOps Administrator - Associate', 'aws-certified-sysops-administrator-associate', '4.5', 'From Uptime to Optimization', '1', NULL, '<p>Becoming an AWS Certified SysOps Administrator - Associate signifies an advanced level of proficiency in managing, operating, and optimizing systems on the AWS platform. This certification exam is designed to validate candidates\' technical expertise in deployment, management, and operations on AWS, ensuring they can deliver the stability, automation, and security required by businesses in the cloud.</p>\r\n<p>To excel in the AWS Certified SysOps Administrator - Associate exam, candidates must possess a deep understanding of deployment and management practices, including transferring existing on-premises applications to AWS, controlling data flows, and implementing cost control mechanisms. Key areas of knowledge include selecting appropriate AWS services based on requirements, understanding operational best practices, estimating AWS usage costs, and identifying cost optimization strategies.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The exam blueprint outlines seven domains, each with a specific weightage:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Monitoring and Metrics (15%)</li>\r\n<li>High Availability (15%)</li>\r\n<li>Analysis (15%)</li>\r\n<li>Deployment and Provisioning (15%)</li>\r\n<li>Data Management (12%)</li>\r\n<li>Security (15%)</li>\r\n<li>Networking (13%)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Preparation for this certification involves gaining at least one year of hands-on experience with the AWS platform, including managing and operating production systems. Candidates should have a firm grasp of AWS tenets, hands-on experience with the AWS CLI and SDKs/API tools, and a strong understanding of network technologies and security concepts as they relate to AWS.</p>\r\n<p>Candidates can prepare for the exam through resources such as the SysOps on AWS course, AWS Cloud Computing White Papers, and AWS documentation. Additionally, familiarity with virtualization technology, monitoring and auditing systems, and collaborating with developers and business teams is crucial for success.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The exam consists of multiple-choice and multiple-response questions, and candidates have 80 minutes to complete it. It is available in multiple languages, including English, Japanese, Brazilian Portuguese, and Simplified Chinese.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To be eligible for the exam, candidates must have at least one year of experience operating AWS-based applications, along with the ability to provision, operate, and maintain systems running on AWS. By mastering AWS SysOps administration and obtaining the Certified SysOps Administrator - Associate certification, professionals can demonstrate their expertise in cloud operations and open doors to exciting career opportunities in cloud computing.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cost: USD 150 for exam registration, and USD 20 for practice exam registration.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '30 Hours', 45000.00, 3080.00, 840.00, 0.00, 'AWS Certified SysOps Administrator - Associate', 'AWS Certified SysOps Administrator - Associate', 'AWS Certified SysOps Administrator - Associate', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:34:05', 'courses/hHVkfqKxI7qXSFvEvsLRqObLe5d5jEMNi0aBSC51.webp', NULL),
(39, 1, 'CBAP Certification Training', 'cbap-certification-training', '4.5', 'Smart Analysis Starts Here.', '1', NULL, '<p>CBAP Certification Training offered by Digicrome provides a comprehensive preparation program for aspiring business analysts aiming to achieve the esteemed Certified Business Analysis Professional (CBAP) certification. This course equips participants with an extensive understanding of the tools, terminology, and practical skills essential for success in the field of business analysis.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Digicrome?</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Digicrome stands out as a premier training provider committed to empowering individuals to pursue their career aspirations. Our curriculum is meticulously crafted to align with industry trends, ensuring a contemporary learning experience. With a holistic approach to learning, we focus on the holistic development of participants throughout their journey. Our classes feature automatic recording, enabling participants to revisit the content for reinforcement at their convenience.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Objectives of CBAP Certification:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Gain a deep understanding of business analysis principles and practices.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Learn to apply business analysis techniques effectively in real-world scenarios.</li>\r\n<li>Acquire expert knowledge in the field, earning recognition within the Business Analysis community.</li>\r\n<li>Enhance your professional profile and potentially increase your salary by up to 13%.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Eligibility Criteria:</strong><br><br><strong>The CBAP course caters to a wide range of professionals, including:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Requirement engineers<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Product owners</li>\r\n<li>System analysts</li>\r\n<li>Product managers</li>\r\n<li>Process analysts</li>\r\n<li>Data analysts</li>\r\n<li>Management consultants</li>\r\n<li>Enterprise analysts</li>\r\n<li>Business system analysts</li>\