(40, 1, 'Program Management Professional Certification Training', 'program-management-professional-certification-training-pgmp', '4.7', 'Strategic Minds Choose PgMP.', '1', NULL, '<p>Program Management Professional Certification Training, offered by Digicrome, is designed for individuals aspiring to excel in the role of Program Manager within organizations. A Program Manager plays a crucial role in ensuring the seamless execution of assigned tasks to achieve unified and desired results for the organization. This certification equips candidates with the necessary skills and competencies to effectively manage multiple projects aligned with organizational objectives.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Objectives of Program Management Professional Certification Training:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Develop competency in stakeholder management, resource management, escalation, benefits realization, prioritization, and governance.</li>\r\n<li>Gain comprehension of complex organizational activities and promote better integration and coordination of multiple projects to achieve desired outcomes.</li>\r\n<li>Identify and acknowledge program lifecycles to enhance project management efficiency.</li>\r\n<li>Recognize and address complications associated with the implementation of large-scale projects in real-world environments.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Prerequisites for Program Management Professional Certification Training:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Candidates must meet the following prerequisites:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Secondary degree: 6,000 hours of certified Project Management Professional (PMP) experience and 10,500 hours of Program Management Professional (PgMP) experience.<br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Four-year degree: 6,000 hours of certified PMP experience and 6,000 hours of certified PgMP experience.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Program Management Professional Examination Format:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Panel review.</li>\r\n<li>Total duration: 4 hours.</li>