(41, 1, 'safeÂ ® 5 advanced scrum master certification training', 'safeÂ ® 5 advanced scrum master certification training', 'a41', NULL, 'Yes', NULL, '<p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Embark on a transformative journey with our SAFe® 5 Advanced Scrum Master Certification Training, meticulously designed by Digicrome to empower learners with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in the SAFe® 5 Advanced Scrum Master (SASM) exam on their very first attempt. This comprehensive course delves into the pivotal role a Scrum Master plays in a SAFe® enterprise, unravelling the intricacies of leading high-performance agile teams and applying SAFe® principles at an enterprise level.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\"><b>Course Highlights:</b></span><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\"><b>Duration:</b></span><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\"> Immerse yourself in 16 hours of intensive training over two days (8 hours per day).</span><br></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Material:</b> Access in-house published course material tailored for optimal learning.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Professional Development:</b> Earn 16 crucial Professional Development Units (PDUs), essential for the SAFe Advanced Scrum Master certification.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Interactive Learning:</b> Interact with expert instructors who bring contemporary tactics to the forefront.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Problem Solving: </b>Sharpen your innovative thinking ability, providing out-of-the-box solutions for real-world scenarios.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Why Choose Digicrome?</b></span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">At Digicrome, our commitment to developing well-rounded individuals is unwavering. Our faculty, possessing high levels of expertise, employ modern teaching methods for effective training. With 24x7 guidance via call, email, or video, participants can seamlessly navigate the learning journey. Experience demo classes for a preview of the engaging sessions.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Main Objectives of the SAFe Advanced Scrum Master Certification Training:</b></span></p><ol><li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Gain insights into managing teams and applying the Scaled Scrum framework.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Master effective Agile coaching principles for a multi-team environment.</span></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Develop solutions for Agile and Scrum anti-patterns.</span></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Facilitate the adoption of Agile architecture, DevOps, and engineering practices.</span></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Harness Kanban techniques for sustaining continuous workflow.</span></li></ol><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Prerequisites:</b></span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">To embark on this certification, candidates must hold one of the following certifications:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Professional Scrum Master (PSM)</span><br></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">SAFe Scrum Master (SSM)</span></li></ul><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\"><b>Target Audience:</b></span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Ideal for team leaders, project managers, Agile coaches, existing Scrum Masters, and engineering managers in a SAFe® or enterprise Agile context.</span></p><p class=\"selectable-text copyable-text iq0m558w g0rxnol2\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\"><b>Examination Format:</b></span><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">60 multiple-choice questions</span><br></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">2 hours duration</span></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Passing criteria: 70% (42 correct answers)</span></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">English language</span></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Web-based, closed-book examination</span></li><li><span class=\"selectable-text copyable-text\">Exam retake charges: $50</span></li></ul><p 