(42, 1, 'Spanish language Training A1 (Beginner)', 'spanish-language-training-a1-beginner', '4.6', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>A1 - By the end of this level a language learner can introduce oneself or someone else , they can ask and form questions about home , family , neighbourhood , surrounding, food etc. The Objective is to equip students with basic communication skills and lay foundation of language. In this level they will be able to make day to day communication, they will learn about present tense and they can easily make small conversations.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '40 Hours', 50000.00, 2200.00, 600.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-25 15:00:11', 'https://www.digicromeacademy.com/assets/images/inner-img/course-thumb5.webp', NULL);
