(43, 1, 'Spanish language Training A2( Elementary )', 'spanish-language-training-a2-elementary', '4.7', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>A2-By the end of this level a language learner will be able to communicate in simple and routine task,they can easily describe experience and expressions Level A2 corresponds to basic users of the language, i.e. learns are able to communciate in everyday situations with commonly-used expressions and elementary vocabulary. They will be learning future tense which will help in better communication.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '40 Hours', 45000.00, 1980.00, 540.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-25 15:00:26', 'https://www.digicromeacademy.com/assets/images/inner-img/course-thumb5.webp', NULL),
(44, 3, 'Spanish language Training B1 (Intermediate Level)', 'spanish-language-training-b1-intermediate-level', '4.8', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>B1-By the end of this level a language learner will be able to talk fluently at intermediate level. They will be Familiar with the topics of work place, school, home , leisure etc They can write essays expressing thoughts and ideas. Students can understand straightforward texts on subjects related to their fields of interest. They can find and understand general information they need in everyday material, such as letters, brochures and short official documents.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '50 Hours', 60000.00, 2640.00, 720.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-07 14:53:31', 'courses/JcLWZWDRMpooSifHvKYoYk5purNiSQsQHORyvFNo.webp', NULL),
(45, 3, 'Spanish language Training B2 (Upper Intermediate)', 'spanish-language-training-b2-upper-intermediate', '4.9', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>B2-By the end of this level a language learner will be able to distinguish all the tenses and make coherent , fluent conversation with native speakers. They Can work in corporates and companies requiring minimum B2 level. Level B2 corresponds to a more advanced, more independent level than previous levels. A B2 user can communicate easily and spontaneously in a clear and detailed manner.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '50 Hours', 65000.00, 2860.00, 780.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-07 14:53:58', 'courses/BLjVdKw4Tc3vaZvSLXauO5veGSoQyZVPqoc7lfiB.webp', NULL),
(46, 3, 'Spanish language Training C1 (Proficient-advance)', 'spanish-language-training-c1-proficient-advance', '4.7', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>C1-By the end of this level a language learner can do complex dialogue writing , Spontaneous participation with natives, they can handle personal situations(formal , informal ) and can conduct debates on day to day topics. They can talk fluently, spontaneously and almost effortlessly produce and co-produce a wide range of extensive, clear and detailed spoken texts that are conceptually and structurally complex, in various registers with appropriate intonation and accents. Students Can easily work in corporates and companies.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '60 Hours', 65000.00, 2860.00, 780.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-07 15:47:31', 'courses/EvDjxYcOVOisXzmMkX1tcD95Ptx5dRwYUXGj1NCg.webp', NULL),
(47, 3, 'Spanish language Training C2 (Master- Level)', 'spanish-language-training-c2-master-level', '4.6', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>At the culmination of this advanced level, language learners will exhibit unparalleled mastery and fluency in Spanish, capable of seamlessly navigating any linguistic challenge or social context. With native-like proficiency, they will effortlessly express themselves with precision and eloquence, adapting effortlessly to diverse situations.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Expressive Fluency:</strong> Learners at the C2 level possess the ability to articulate thoughts and ideas with unparalleled fluency and accuracy, conveying complex concepts with ease and clarity.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Native-like Proficiency:</strong> Having attained a level of proficiency akin to that of a native speaker, students demonstrate a deep understanding of the Spanish language and culture, effortlessly integrating into Spanish-speaking environments.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Adaptability:</strong> Proficient in Spanish at the C2 level, learners exhibit remarkable adaptability, seamlessly adjusting their language use to suit any context or audience, whether formal or informal.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Effective Communication:</strong> With the capability to provide a logical structure and coherent narrative, C2-level students excel in producing clear, articulate, and sophisticated reports, articles, essays, and critical analyses, enriching their discourse with nuanced insights and perspectives.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Elevate your Spanish language skills to the pinnacle of proficiency with our C2 level program, unlocking boundless opportunities for professional and personal growth in the Spanish-speaking world.<br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '60 Hours', 65000.00, 2860.00, 780.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-27 14:08:38', 'courses/oVOeJhzKUAaums6opbqlooVAjyVp1oKgHTV1tsJQ.webp', NULL),
(48, 3, 'Japanese Language N5-Basic (MINNA NO NIHONGO)', 'japanese-language-n5-basic-minna-no-nihongo', '4.5', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>1. N5 - MINNA NO NIHONGO 2. 100HRS (CHAPTER 1 TO 25), 120 KANJI CHARACTERS 3. LISTENING CLASSES</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '100HRS (CHAPTER 1 TO 25)', 75000.00, 3300.00, 900.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-07 15:48:14', 'courses/b127BXsc9b5N21irx030IXvVaO8swj5AP0M90ynP.webp', NULL),
(49, 3, 'Japanese Language N4 (MINNA NO NIHONGO)', 'japanese-language-n4-minna-no-nihongo', '5', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>1. N4- MINNA NO NIHONGO 2. 120hrs chapter 25 to 50 3. 200+ kanji Characters 4. Listening Classes</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '120 Hours', 75000.00, 3300.00, 900.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-07 15:48:40', 'courses/uh4q8RP7uJQt8EeDw0BwyWUjNGVzz4GZeKJ4KuYj.webp', NULL),
(50, 3, 'Japanese Language N3 (TRIO & Shinkansen)', 'japanese-language-n3-trio-and-shinkansen', '4.8', NULL, '1', NULL, '<p>Dive into the intricacies of Japanese language proficiency with our comprehensive N3 course, combining the power of TRIO and Shinkansen methodologies to accelerate your learning journey.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>8 Months, 400+ Hours:</strong> Over 8 months and more than 400 hours of immersive instruction, master the essentials of Japanese grammar, vocabulary, and conversational skills required to navigate real-world scenarios with confidence.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kanji Characters:</strong> Gain proficiency in Kanji characters, a fundamental aspect of Japanese writing, through our structured lessons and interactive exercises designed to reinforce recognition and application.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Listening Classes:</strong> Sharpen your listening comprehension skills with dedicated classes focused on enhancing your ability to understand spoken Japanese in various contexts, from everyday conversations to formal settings.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Experience the fusion of TRIO and Shinkansen methodologies in our N3 course, designed to equip you with the language skills and cultural insights needed to thrive in Japanese-speaking environments. With our expert instruction and immersive approach, embark on a transformative journey towards Japanese language proficiency.<br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '8months 400+ Hours', 75000.00, 3300.00, 900.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-27 14:09:08', 'courses/SOptPkTUBSv5jhGq1axuT1X4EZhH4QsgXD7O55gb.webp', NULL),
(51, 1, 'Machine Learning', 'data-science-with-machine-learning', '4.9', 'Turning Data into Intelligence.', '1', NULL, '<p>Data science is a multidisciplinary field that focuses on studying and analyzing data to extract valuable insights and make informed decisions. It involves various processes such as data collection, cleaning, visualization, and statistical analysis to uncover patterns and trends within the data. Data scientists often use tools like Python and R for data manipulation and analysis.</p>\r\n<p>Machine learning, on the other hand, is a subfield of artificial intelligence (AI) that focuses on developing algorithms and models that can learn from historical data and make predictions or decisions without being explicitly programmed. Machine learning techniques include supervised learning (classification and regression), unsupervised learning (clustering and dimensionality reduction), and reinforcement learning.</p>\r\n<p>Don\'t miss the chance to join the ranks of professionals shaping the future with data. Invest in your education, and you\'ll unlock a world of opportunities in Data Science and Machine Learning. Enrol today to make your mark in this exciting and rapidly evolving field!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Are you ready to take the first step towards an exhilarating career in Data Science and Machine Learning? Join us and embark on this transformative journey today!</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '01 Months', 30000.00, 1325.56, 360.80, 0.00, 'Data Science & Machine Learning', 'Data Science & Machine Learning', 'Program Overview:\r\nData science is a field that studies data and how to extract meaning from it, whereas machine learning is a field that learns from historical data and is used it to build classification, regressors and clusters of data. Machine learning is a branch of artificial intelligence.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-27 14:09:19', 'courses/oSm7NXSoOjEsmvfOWLaSwQ6fNl7KP0ZFCa80vMmy.webp', NULL),
(52, 1, 'Power BI / Tableau', 'Power-bi-Tableau', '4.7', 'From Dashboards to Decisions.', '1', NULL, '<p><strong>Power BI:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Power BI is a cutting-edge business intelligence and data visualization tool developed by Microsoft. It is renowned for its user-friendly interface and robust analytics capabilities, making it a top choice for organizations seeking to leverage their data effectively. Power BI\'s key features include seamless data integration from various sources, a comprehensive suite of visualization options, and powerful data transformation capabilities.</p>\r\n<p>One of Power BI\'s standout features is its integration with Microsoft\'s ecosystem, allowing users to seamlessly connect with other Microsoft tools like Excel, Azure, and SharePoint. This integration fosters efficient collaboration and data sharing within organizations. Power BI\'s natural language query functionality also stands out, enabling users to ask questions in plain language and receive relevant data insights.</p>\r\n<p>Power Query, an embedded ETL tool, empowers users to clean, shape, and transform data before analysis. The platform offers robust security features, including role-based access control and data encryption, ensuring data privacy and compliance.</p>\r\n<p>With its intuitive drag-and-drop interface, Power BI caters to both technical and non-technical users, enabling them to create interactive reports and dashboards effortlessly. Whether visualizing historical data or performing real-time analysis, Power BI equips businesses with the tools needed to make data-driven decisions and gain a competitive edge.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tableau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tableau is a leading data visualization and business intelligence tool renowned for its simplicity and advanced analytical capabilities. It empowers organizations to transform complex data into actionable insights and interactive visualizations. Tableau\'s strengths lie in its data connectivity, visual exploration, and data blending capabilities.</p>\r\n<p>Tableau excels in data connectivity, offering compatibility with various data sources, including databases, spreadsheets, and cloud services. Its intuitive drag-and-drop interface encourages users to explore data visually, creating interactive dashboards and reports effortlessly. The platform also supports advanced analytics through integration with R and Python, enabling users to perform statistical and predictive analysis.</p>\r\n<p>Data blending is a standout feature of Tableau, allowing users to merge data from multiple sources to create a unified view for comprehensive analysis. Additionally, Tableau Server and Tableau Online facilitate secure sharing and collaboration, enabling users to publish and distribute reports within organizations or to external stakeholders.</p>\r\n<p>Customization options enable users to tailor visualizations and dashboards to their specific needs, fostering a unique reporting experience. Tableau\'s ability to transform data into easily digestible visual narratives empowers organizations to make data-driven decisions, identify trends, and drive business growth in an increasingly data-driven world.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '01 Months', 30000.00, 1325.56, 360.80, 0.00, 'Power BI/Tableau: Choose Right Tool for Your Analytics Needs', NULL, 'Utilise Power BI/Tableau to learn about the possibilities of data visualisation! Get insights, make intelligent choices, and create visually stunning output.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:29:32', 'courses/otYOpiO6agrY50jwZDVAVMCrRSTXsoZpUvNfVib4.webp', NULL),
(53, 1, 'Python', 'pg-program-data-science-with-python', '4.6', 'The Power Behind Modern Tech', '1', NULL, '<p>Data science is a field that studies data and how to extract meaning from it, whereas machine learning is a field that learns from historical data and is used to build classification, regressors and clusters of data. Python is a high-level, general-purpose programming language. Its design philosophy emphasizes code readability with the use of significant indentation. Python is dynamically typed and garbage-collected. It supports multiple programming paradigms, including structured, object-oriented and functional programming.<br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '1 Months', 30000.00, 1325.56, 360.80, 0.00, 'Data Science with Python – Learn from Basics to Advance', 'data-science-and-python', 'Master Python and Data Science tools to launch your career. Learn data handling, analysis, visualization, and machine learning with hands-on practice.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-01 16:50:13', 'courses/CgtwBwIh3KCusiY3mKXHNaCIDtnf5kehNtYwotlm.webp', NULL),
(54, 1, 'MY SQL', 'pg-program-in-mysql', '4.8', 'From Queries to Clarity.', '1', NULL, '<p>MySQL is a powerful and widely used open-source relational database management system that plays a pivotal role in the world of business analytics. With its robust features and capabilities, MySQL serves as a critical component in handling and analyzing vast amounts of data for organizations of all sizes.</p>\r\n<p>One of MySQL\'s primary strengths lies in its scalability and performance. It can efficiently manage large datasets, making it an ideal choice for businesses dealing with extensive data sources. This scalability ensures that as an organization grows, MySQL can adapt and continue to deliver fast and reliable data retrieval and storage.</p>\r\n<p>Data integrity and security are paramount in business analytics, and MySQL excels in these aspects. It offers various authentication mechanisms, encryption options, and access control features to safeguard sensitive business data. This level of security is vital when handling proprietary and confidential information for strategic decision-making.</p>\r\n<p>Furthermore, MySQL supports complex querying and data manipulation, making it well-suited for analytical tasks. Its support for structured query language (SQL) allows analysts and data professionals to extract valuable insights by crafting intricate queries and aggregations. MySQL also supports various indexing techniques to optimize query performance, ensuring that data analysis remains efficient even with extensive datasets.</p>\r\n<p>The extensibility of MySQL through user-defined functions and stored procedures enables businesses to tailor their analytics solutions to specific needs. This flexibility is invaluable in creating custom analytics applications and automating data processing tasks.</p>\r\n<p>In conclusion, MySQL is an indispensable tool in the realm of business analytics. Its scalability, security, performance, and versatility make it an ideal choice for organizations looking to harness the power of data analysis to inform strategic decision-making. Whether examining past business data or real-time information, MySQL empowers businesses to leverage their data effectively and gain a competitive edge in today\'s data-driven landscape.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '1 Months', 30000.00, 1325.56, 360.80, 0.00, 'MySQL Course Online – Learn Database Management', 'MY SQL Course, MySQL Course Online', 'Join our MySQL course to learn database creation, queries, joins, and optimization. Build real SQL skills for data analysis and backend development.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-08 16:30:43', 'courses/RxcbbLFkI4J1VeZ5HqAu4PKbH50V7I10haDv2hNX.webp', NULL),
(55, 1, 'Advanced Certification Online Data Analytics and ML Course', 'online-data-analytics-and-machine-learning-program', '4.8', 'Get Ready for Top Data Science Jobs', '1', 'browser_pdfs/MmEprxAAZPKGSlevy2ZNl4sHZiwEAUFjyDYVfTPY.pdf', '<p>In the rapidly evolving landscape of technology, data science and machine learning have emerged as indispensable fields, driving innovation and insights across industries. Digicrome\'s Advanced Certification online program in Data Science and Machine Learning is a comprehensive course designed to equip professionals and enthusiasts with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in this dynamic domain.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Opt for an Advanced Certification Online in Data Science &amp; Machine Learning?</strong></p>\r\n<p>The proliferation of data has transformed how businesses operate, making data science and machine learning essential skills. This advanced certification program provides a structured learning path, covering key concepts and tools required to analyze and derive meaningful insights from vast datasets.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Digicrome\'s Advanced Certification Program in Data Science &amp; Machine Learning:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Digicrome\'s program stands out as a beacon for those seeking an in-depth understanding of these transformative technologies. Crafted to cater to both professionals seeking career advancement and individuals aspiring to enter the field, this program offers the following&nbsp;<br><strong>key highlights:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Comprehensive Curriculum:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The program covers a broad spectrum of topics, including Python, exploratory data analysis, machine learning, deep learning, and more. The curriculum ensures a natural progression, gradually introducing learners to interconnected facets of data science.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Expert Faculty:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Delivered by industry leaders and subject matter experts, the program\'s immersive lectures utilize advanced technological tools for a seamless learning experience. Dedicated program managers provide support beyond the curriculum.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hands-On Learning:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Assignments and projects are integral to the program, allowing participants to test their skills and apply newly acquired knowledge constructively. Instructors provide detailed feedback, fostering active participation and skill development.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Networking Opportunities:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The program facilitates networking among learners, connecting them with peers, mentors, and industry professionals. Communication channels, including email, voice calls, and video calls, enhance the online learning experience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Flexible Support:</strong></p>\r\n<p>One-on-one doubt-clearing sessions, coupled with email, voice call, and video call support, ensure participants navigate the course smoothly. The dedicated support system covers both study material-related doubts and managerial queries.</p>\r\n<p>Embark on a transformative journey in the world of data science and machine learning with Digicrome\'s Advanced Certification Program. Gain a competitive edge in these high-demand fields, enrich your career prospects, and become an expert in harnessing data for valuable insights and innovation. Join the program to stay ahead in technology and make a meaningful impact in the data-driven landscape. Elevate your skills, advance your career, and be a leader in the dynamic field of data science and machine learning.</p>', 'banner/qJDSayTrb0pk92Nohco4bx6bKgkbQfJRfGgR87Pe.webp', 'This online advanced certification in Data Analytics and Machine Learning, in six months of training, will teach you data handling, analysis, and machine learning in real-world situations and projects under the guidance of seasoned experts. The course teaches key tools and techniques specific to data and ML, like Python, and EDA, to make you efficient in decisions for businesses and give them a direction. Apply to this course and upskill into roles of extensive demand and growth. Get certified today.', 0, 1, '3', '12-07-2025', '06-Month Online Program', 60000.00, 2536.99, 690.92, 0.00, 'Online Machine Learning Course with Certificate', 'Data Science and Machine Learning Course, Best Course for Machine Learning, Machine Learning Online Course, Machine Learning Certification Course, Machine Learning in Data Science, Machine Learning Course with Certificate, ML Course, Machine Learning Cour', 'Digicrome offers the Best Machine Learning Course with Placement. Enroll in this certification course and clear all your doubts with a 1:1 session.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-07-12 09:59:58', 'courses/1TO4XpvADUEmkw9pZcosNzoFuNXdupcYlFWpLboV.webp', NULL),
(56, 1, 'Master\'s Program in Big Data Engineering & Cloud Computing', 'master-s-program-in-big-data-engineering-cloud-computing', '4.9', 'Master the Future: Big Data & Cloud Computing', '1', 'browser_pdfs/bvEefykSXni7F64s7IMBXmcMQeAbZ7NKKNlvEaTG.pdf', '<p>The Master\'s Program in Big Data Engineering &amp; Cloud Computing offered by Digicrome is designed to equip professionals with advanced skills and knowledge in managing and leveraging large-scale data and cloud computing technologies. This comprehensive program integrates theoretical learning with practical hands-on experience, preparing participants to excel in roles such as Big Data Engineers and Cloud Architects.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Focus Areas:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Big Data Engineering:</strong> Gain expertise in handling and processing large volumes of data using cutting-edge technologies like Hadoop, Spark, and Kafka. Learn data modeling, data warehousing, and optimization techniques crucial for effective data management.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cloud Computing:</strong> Explore cloud platforms such as AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud. Master cloud architecture, deployment models, and services essential for designing scalable, secure, and cost-effective cloud solutions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Data Analytics and Machine Learning:</strong> Develop skills in data analysis, predictive modeling, and machine learning algorithms. Understand how to extract valuable insights from data to drive business decisions and innovation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>DevOps and Containerization:</strong> Learn DevOps practices for continuous integration and deployment (CI/CD) in cloud environments. Acquire proficiency in containerization technologies like Docker and Kubernetes for efficient application deployment and management.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Program Structure:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Duration: Flexible, typically spanning 11 Months.</li>\r\n<li>Internship: 3 Months live program</li>\r\n<li>Learning Modes: Blend of online lectures, hands-on labs, and projects.</li>\r\n<li>Capstone Project: Apply acquired skills to solve real-world challenges in big data and cloud computing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Career Opportunities: Graduates of this program can pursue roles such as Big Data Engineer, Cloud Architect, Data Scientist, Machine Learning Engineer, and DevOps Engineer across various industries including technology, finance, healthcare, and e-commerce.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Digicrome?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Industry-aligned curriculum developed in collaboration with experts.</li>\r\n<li>Practical, hands-on learning approach with industry projects and case studies.</li>\r\n<li>Access to a global network of professionals and mentors.</li>\r\n<li>Certification upon successful completion, validating expertise in big data engineering and cloud computing.<br><br>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Join Digicrome\'s Master\'s Program in Big Data Engineering &amp; Cloud Computing to advance your career in the rapidly evolving fields of big data and cloud technology. Contact us today to embark on your journey towards becoming a skilled professional in this dynamic domain.</p>', 'banner/54bUmMtsR09DWLoJ1oTPqaWLggWWRTHFnLSlRUqP.webp', NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '11-Month Online Program', 299000.00, 13149.00, 3580.00, 0.00, 'Big Data Engineering and Cloud Computing Course | Certification', 'Online Data Engineering Course, Big Data Engineering Course, Big Data Engineering and Cloud Computing Course, Data Engineering Course for Beginner, Data Engineering Course Online, Data Engineering Online Training Courses, Data Engineering courses with pla', 'Our Data Engineering Course is designed by industry professionals to upgrade your Data Engineering skills. learn from experts and earn Microsoft certification', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-27 14:13:29', 'courses/jPLomdVsyOpSpRWLuKV9s9uVMNAGIdvllilfn9nb.webp', NULL),
(57, 1, 'Real Estate Business Management Program', 'real-estate-business-management-program', '4.8', 'Upgrade the Future: Real Estate Course', '1', NULL, '<p>Upskill your career in Real Estate. Digicrome provide a&nbsp;<strong>Business Management Course of Real Estate</strong>. It is a certification course with industry experts. We also provide customized training workshops and other management programs for the real estate industry. Digicrome offers world-class best practices, that enables new opportunities in real estate.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Program Benefits</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Industry Experts Lectures</li>\r\n<li>Field visit</li>\r\n<li>Industry project</li>\r\n<li>Exposure to the best real estate practices</li>\r\n<li>Industry Recognized Certificate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The program also enhances the participant\'s business skills through the marketing and sales modules for residential, commercial and retail properties, soft skills and business skills training, an entrepreneurship module and a digital marketing module.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Who Should Enroll?</strong></p>\r\n<p>This program is ideal for:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Aspiring real estate entrepreneurs</li>\r\n<li>Real estate agents and brokers looking to scale their business</li>\r\n<li>Property developers and managers</li>\r\n<li>Investors and financial analysts</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '1', '6 Months', 80000.00, 3469.52, 944.62, 0.00, 'Real Estate Business Management Program | Certification Program | Digicrome', 'Real Estate Course, Real Estate Program, Real Estate Online Course, Online Real Estate Course, Business Management Course of Real Estate', 'Digicrome launches a new online Real Estate Course with job and internship opportunities. Explore a comprehensive curriculum covering a wide range of real estate topics to build a successful career in the industry.', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-06-27 14:13:42', 'courses/dSSnMRl8wA5pSvWzdfpw8wF9zdNdnxcb8FnPovdx.webp', NULL),
