(61, 1, 'Certified Investment Banking & Valuation Analyst (CIBVA)', 'investment-banking-certification-course', '4.9', 'Crack the Code to Investment Banking', '1', 'browser_pdfs/AFK4ppky1Zyqsarr9xeo5ZClOG0QBcnUNkxHsosW.pdf', '<p><strong>Course Overview&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Learn fundamental investment banking skills with the Certified Investment Banking &amp; Valuation Analyst (CIBVA) course by Digicrome and grow in a high-demand career. It is made to make you master key IB skills such as Financial Modeling &amp; Valuation, Advanced Excel &amp; PowerPoint, Pitch Book &amp; Deal Structuring, Industry &amp; Company Research, Presentation &amp; Communication Skills, and more.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This 6-month program will give you hands-on learning and training from experts. It is designed for students or professionals looking to take up finance roles. The training will be conducted through a total of 48 weekend classes. It will prepare you to thrive in roles across M&amp;A, IPO advisory, financial modeling, and valuation analysis.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>What is Investment Banking?</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Investment Banking comes under finance. It is a specialized field and plays a crucial role in raising capital and helping businesses make strategic financial decisions. An investment banker also guides in the market&rsquo;s economic conditions or how a business can be improved. As an Investment Banking Analyst, you&rsquo;ll help with deals, valuation models, and advise clients on big transactions.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Learning Outcomes</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong>By the end of this course, you will:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Master financial modeling, DCF, LBO, and M&amp;A analysis</li>\r\n<li>Create valuation reports and pitchbooks used by top companies.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Analyze IPOs, market trends, and capital structures</li>\r\n<li>Use tools like Bloomberg Terminal, Capital IQ, Tableau &amp; Power BI</li>\r\n<li>Automate finance workflows using Python</li>\