INSERT INTO `faqs` (`id`, `course_id`, `user_id`, `question`, `answer`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(5, 1, 2, 'How is Data Science different from AI?', 'Data Science creates meaning from various data types, while AI uses that information to improve itself and ease decision-making. Together, they help businesses achieve success, improve customer experiences, and stay ahead with well-informed decisions.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(6, 1, 2, 'Do I need programming knowledge for a Data Science and AI course at Digicrome?', 'No, you can apply without programming knowledge. We teach everything from the beginning, starting with Python basics to advanced AI and Machine Learning.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(7, 1, 2, 'What are the requirements for enrolling in a Data Science and AI course at Digicrome?', 'No previous experience is required. Basic computer skills, English comprehension, and an interest in data are enough. Anyone, be it a 12th pass, a graduate, or a postgraduate from any field, can apply.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(8, 1, 2, 'What type of projects will I work on during the Digicrome course?', 'You’ll work on real-life projects like AI chatbots, image classification, sentiment analysis, recommendation systems, and deep learning models to help you develop understanding and showcase your skills.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(9, 1, 2, 'How long does it take to complete a Data Science and AI course at Digicrome?', 'Our Data Science and AI course can be completed within 11 months (200+ hours), and the course curriculum includes a 12-month internship starting from the  2nd month of your course.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(10, 1, 2, 'Will I receive a certificate after course completion from Digicrome?', 'Yes, you will receive a program completion certificate from Digicrome, along with specialized certificates from our course collaborators, Microsoft and IBM, confirming your Data Science & AI skills.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(11, 1, 2, 'Can I take Digicrome\'s course online?', 'Yes, this is a 100% online course in Data Science and AI, taught in English, with LMS access, personal mentorship, and a flexible schedule.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(12, 1, 2, 'What is the condition of the data science and artificial intelligence job market?', 'The AI & Data Science sector is growing significantly, with over 2.3 million job openings by 2027 and merely 1.2 million professionals. There is a huge skill gap, making it the right time to upskill.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(13, 1, 2, 'What support is available during the Digicrome course?', 'Digicrome throughout the course provides support through personal mentoring, weekly doubt sessions, live classes, resume & interview preparation, complete job assistance, lifetime LMS access, soft skills training, project guidance, and more.', '2025-05-17 09:43:54', '2025-05-17 09:43:54'),
(21, 61, 2, 'What is Investment Banking?', 'Investment Banking helps businesses raise capital. It\'s a role through which major financial deals take place. In this, the responsibilities include handling mergers or acquisitions, and creating a network of investors and business groups for planning growth and business strategizing.', '2025-05-31 10:30:08', '2025-05-31 10:30:08'),
(22, 61, 2, 'What will I learn in this Investment Banking Course?', 'This is a comprehensive course that will help you with the main finance skills. Learn topics like financial modeling, company valuation, risk analysis, etc. The course covers everything needed to understand and work in real investment roles.', '2025-05-31 10:30:08', '2025-05-31 10:30:08'),
(23, 61, 2, 'Why Choose this Investment Banking Course from Digicrome?', 'This Course by Digicrome is made to prepare you for realistic investment banking scenarios. You get practical exposure through projects, case studies, and assessments. Learn with expert guidance in live sessions. Open for freshers and working professionals from any industry.', '2025-05-31 10:30:08', '2025-05-31 10:30:08'),
(24, 61, 2, 'Do I need a finance background to join this Investment Banking course?', 'No, it’s not compulsory to come from a finance background. We’ll teach you from the basics to the advanced. But having a strong interest in finance or numbers helps. A basic understanding of finance makes it easier to follow through the course.', '2025-05-31 10:30:08', '2025-05-31 10:30:08'),
(25, 61, 2, 'What skills will I have after completing this course?', 'You will gain the skills needed in top finance roles and are asked by top companies, which include but are not limited to financial modelling, understanding of M&A, valuation, analytical thinking, communication, business understanding, and more.', '2025-05-31 10:30:08', '2025-05-31 10:30:08'),
(26, 61, 2, 'What are the Job Opportunities available after this course?', 'This course can be a great start for a satisfactory career. As you complete it, multiple roles will open for you, such as Investment Banking Analyst, Risk Consultant, and Financial Analyst. The curriculum gives you the right skills and practical exposure.', '2025-05-31 10:30:08', '2025-05-31 10:30:08'),
(27, 61, 2, 'What support is available during the Digicrome course?', 'You get 1:1 mentorship, live doubt-clearing sessions, placement support, resume help, and interview prep. Program managers and expert trainers guide you throughout the course so you never feel stuck while learning or applying for jobs.', '2025-05-31 10:30:08', '2025-05-31 10:30:08'),
(28, 55, 2, 'What is Advanced Certification Online Data Analytics and Machine Learning Course about?', 'This is a 6-month live online program with hands-on work and expert guidance. It teaches you the basics and advanced parts of data, covering how to understand, work with, and analyse data using Python, machine learning, and more.', '2025-06-09 17:02:56', '2025-06-09 17:02:56'),
(29, 55, 2, 'What background knowledge is needed for this course?', 'You can be a 12th pass or a graduate from any accredited institute or a professional looking to enhance their Data and ML skills. It is not mandatory to be from a tech background. We teach everything from beginner to advanced level, step by step.', '2025-06-09 17:02:56', '2025-06-09 17:02:56'),
(30, 55, 2, 'Who should take this course?', 'Anyone interested in Data Analytics & ML or willing to learn and earn from it, be it a student, working professional, or job seeker interested in upskilling regardless of their background, can take this course.', '2025-06-09 17:02:56', '2025-06-09 17:02:56'),
(31, 55, 2, 'What will I learn in this course?', 'This course teaches you all the tools, methods, and techniques used in data analytics and the role of ML in it. You will learn Python, data analysis, data visualization, machine learning, and deep learning through practical experience with capstone projects and assessments.', '2025-06-09 17:02:56', '2025-06-09 17:02:56'),
(32, 55, 2, 'Will I get a certificate after completing the course?', 'Yes, you will be certified after course completion. You can share it on your LinkedIn or include it in your resume. This will enhance your job opportunities and make you industry-ready and credible for roles in Data Analytics and Machine Learning.', '2025-06-09 17:02:56', '2025-06-09 17:02:56'),
(33, 55, 2, 'What kind of support will I get during the course?', 'Throughout the course, you will be supported in various ways, including 1-on-1 guidance, regular doubt sessions, and dedicated program managers. You will be prepared for job interviews through mock sessions and will also be equipped with the necessary soft skills. Additionally, mentors will be available through calls, emails, and video calls throughout the course.', '2025-06-09 17:02:56', '2025-06-09 17:02:56'),
(34, 55, 2, 'What career opportunities can I expect after this course?', 'You can apply for roles like Data Analyst, Business Analyst, ML Engineer, or Data Scientist. These are high-demand roles across all industries — from tech to finance to healthcare.', '2025-06-09 17:02:56', '2025-06-09 17:02:56'),
(35, 3, 2, '1. Is this an advanced program, or is it suitable for beginners too?', 'This course is for anyone looking to switch careers, grow in AI & ML, or be a fresh graduate. It starts from the basics, goes to advanced, and adds practical learning. An AI or data background is not mandatory.', '2025-06-09 17:04:44', '2025-06-09 17:04:44'),
(36, 3, 2, '2.  Do I need coding experience to start?', 'No, you are eligible to apply without prior coding skills. Learn Python basics and slowly move to advanced topics. You will be getting expert mentorship through the weekends alongside weekly doubt-clearing sessions.', '2025-06-09 17:04:44', '2025-06-09 17:04:44'),
(37, 3, 2, '3. How is this course different from others?', 'The course is not just theory. It includes practical projects, real case studies, and regular assessments. The course curriculum is set in a way that you will be practicing in every module.', '2025-06-09 17:04:44', '2025-06-09 17:04:44'),
(38, 3, 2, '4. What topics are covered in the course?', 'With Every Topic You will learn the skills to become an expert in Data Science & AI. The syllabus includes topics like Python, SQL, ML, Deep Learning, NLP, and more. You Will get relevant projects and real-life case studies for practical learning.', '2025-06-09 17:04:44', '2025-06-09 17:04:44'),
(39, 3, 2, '5. What’s the course duration and mode?', 'This course is a complete online certification program. The training will be online by experts over the weekends. You can choose batch time as per your schedule. Moreover, you can complete it in 9 months or less at your own speed.', '2025-06-09 17:04:44', '2025-06-09 17:04:44'),
(40, 3, 2, '6. Will I get a certificate after completing the course?', 'Yes, complete the course to receive a globally valid certificate in collaboration with Microsoft. This will help you gain credibility and validation for your AI & ML skills and increase job opportunities.', '2025-06-09 17:04:44', '2025-06-09 17:04:44'),
(41, 3, 2, '7.  Will I get placement assistance?', 'Yes, you will get full placement assistance and guide for job interviews, resume creation, and soft skills excellence. We will prepare you for the industry assisting you to get placed in a relevant role.', '2025-06-09 17:04:44', '2025-06-09 17:04:44'),
(42, 58, 2, '1. What is this Post Graduate Program in Data Science with Generative AI program about?', 'This is a 12-month online program that will equip learners with high-demand skills in data science and generative AI. The course includes live sessions, hands-on practice through projects, and a six-month internship. Moreover, it also includes placement assistance to help you get placed in a  relevant role.', '2025-06-10 09:50:43', '2025-06-10 09:50:43'),
(43, 58, 2, '2. What is the eligibility for this course?', 'Anyone can apply. The prerequisite is only to be a graduate from any domain, with basic computer knowledge. It is not mandatory to be from a technical background. You can be from humanities, commerce, or maths and science; you will gain mastery starting from the basics and gradually move to advanced Data Science and Generative AI.', '2025-06-10 09:50:43', '2025-06-10 09:50:43'),
(44, 58, 2, '3. Is this course beginner-friendly?', 'Yes, this course is for all levels, as herein a fresh graduate can gain new skills or a professional can expand existing skills. You\'ll begin with Excel, Python, SQL, then move to Machine Learning, Deep Learning, NLP, Time Series, Generative AI and more sub topics in deep.', '2025-06-10 09:50:43', '2025-06-10 09:50:43'),
(45, 58, 2, '4. What kind of placement support is provided?', 'You will be getting complete job assistance, including resume building, mock interviews, LinkedIn help, and personalized guidance. We will prepare you to get the right jobs of your preference.', '2025-06-10 09:50:43', '2025-06-10 09:50:43'),
(46, 58, 2, '5. What career options are available after completing this course?', 'Complete this course and you’ll have opportunities like data scientists, AI specialists, ML engineers, business analysts, and more, roles in demand across industries like e-commerce, health, and finance. The pay and growth are high, as there is a lack of skilled professionals, but high industry demand.', '2025-06-10 09:50:43', '2025-06-10 09:50:43'),
(47, 58, 2, '6. Why should I choose this course over others?', 'This course covers the modern Data Science industry demands. It teaches generative AI alongside and assures you receive expert-led live classes, projects, and career assistance. Moreover, it includes an internship for practical exposure and can be opted by both beginners and upskillers.', '2025-06-10 09:50:43', '2025-06-10 09:50:43'),
(48, 59, 2, '1. What is this Professional Certification Course in Data Science with Machine Learning by Digicrome about?', 'Become a part of this professional certification course in Data Science with Machine Learning. And within six months, you will be skilled at advanced level, starting from the basics in tools and techniques needed in this field, like Python and Big Data, along with certifications from Digichrome, IBM, and Microsoft.', '2025-06-10 09:52:57', '2025-06-10 09:52:57'),
(49, 59, 2, '2. Who is the right candidate for this online certification program?', 'This course can be taken up by anyone who is interested in data science. You can be an early career professional, a recent graduate, an analyst, or someone looking to switch careers. The flexible structure allows both beginners and experienced learners to grasp and begin their careers in this field.', '2025-06-10 09:52:57', '2025-06-10 09:52:57'),
(50, 59, 2, '3. How does the course structure facilitate effective learning?', 'The course is diversified. It ensures you learn not just theory but practically, using live sessions, hands-on projects, expert-led training, and career assistance. The structure is divided into modules covering Python, SQL, etc. It takes you from the basics to real-world understanding.', '2025-06-10 09:52:57', '2025-06-10 09:52:57'),
(51, 59, 2, '4. What skills will I gain upon this course completion?', 'Within the six-month time frame, you will be skilled enough to help companies make business decisions with your data insights. You will be skilled at data visualization, wrangling, model building, machine learning, etc. You will be a professional data analyzer with predictive model understanding.', '2025-06-10 09:52:57', '2025-06-10 09:52:57'),
(52, 59, 2, '5. What is the prerequisite for this course?', 'No previous background in data science is needed. The requirement is to be curious enough in data and have a bachelor\'s degree from any accredited institution. The course starts from fundamentals, so it\'s free to be taken by a complete beginner. Moreover, it can be taken up by any intermediate learner as well who is looking for better career opportunities and growth.', '2025-06-10 09:52:57', '2025-06-10 09:52:57'),
(53, 59, 2, '6. How will this certification improve my chances of getting employed in the current job market?', 'No previous background in data science is needed. The requirement is to be curious enough in data and have a bachelor\'s degree from any accredited institution. The course starts from fundamentals, so it can be taken by a complete beginner or any professional as well looking for better career opportunities and growth.', '2025-06-10 09:52:57', '2025-06-10 09:52:57'),
(54, 59, 2, '7. What support does Digicrome provide for career advancement after this Professional', 'We help you through career assistance, including resume preparation, mock interviews, and one-on-one guidance. With placement support and partnerships with 500+ companies, you get hired in roles matching your interests. We ensure a smooth transition into data science roles.', '2025-06-10 09:52:57', '2025-06-10 09:52:57'),
(55, 60, 2, '1, How is this course different from a regular AI or ML certification?', 'Most AI and ML courses stick to the basics or theory. This course goes further with complete project deployment and a capstone project that gives you experience like building a real product. You gain hands-on experience in transformers, GANs, and autoencoders. If your target is product or research roles, this is for you.', '2025-06-10 09:55:16', '2025-06-10 09:55:16'),
(56, 60, 2, '2. I’m already working in IT. Will this course still add value?', 'This course can significantly help you if you are making your transition to AI-specific roles. It will train you in tools like TensorFlow, PyTorch, and HuggingFace, along with Cloud Deployment. These are some of the key needs for an AI engineer or MLOps job', '2025-06-10 09:55:16', '2025-06-10 09:55:16'),
(57, 60, 2, '3. Will I learn to build real-world AI products like ChatGPT or DALL·E?', 'Yes, the final project includes building a multi-modal AI assistant. You will use transformers, diffusion models, and APIs, structured exactly like popular AI tools such as ChatGPT or image generators like DALL·E, giving real product-building experience.', '2025-06-10 09:55:16', '2025-06-10 09:55:16'),
(58, 60, 2, '4. Can this course help me become a Generative AI specialist?', 'You can be a generative AI specialist after completing this course, as the curriculum includes topics often asked for by top companies. It covers broad areas like RAG transformers, RLHF, LoRa, GANs, and multi-modal systems, a must for industry roles.', '2025-06-10 09:55:16', '2025-06-10 09:55:16'),
(59, 60, 2, '5. Does this course offer hands-on training, or is it mostly theory?', 'This course focuses on both practice and theory. It makes sure you learn completely hands-on and use the relevant industry tools and technologies. The course includes 48+ live sessions with every topic from classification to transformers and more.', '2025-06-10 09:55:16', '2025-06-10 09:55:16'),
(60, 60, 2, '6. What job roles are available in the market after this course?', 'A wide range of opportunities will open up for you as you complete the course. This includes AI Engineer, Generative AI Developer, and Data Scientist. You become eligible for over 30 job profiles, including roles in research and development.', '2025-06-10 09:55:16', '2025-06-10 09:55:16'),
(61, 60, 2, '7. Is this course suitable if I want to shift from non-tech or analytics to core AI?', 'Yes, the course is designed for every level of learner, be it a beginner or an intermediate. It starts from the foundations and by the 6th month grows to the expert level. Many non-tech learners have also made easy transitions to full-time AI engineering roles.', '2025-06-10 09:55:16', '2025-06-10 09:55:16'),
(62, 66, 2, 'Is this a good Data Science Program for beginners?', 'Yes, this Data Science course in Pune can easily be opted by a complete beginner. It is created in a way that even if your background is non-tech but any other domain, you will grasp it. We start from the basics and slowly upgrade your level through this 11-month course.', '2025-06-14 16:29:26', '2025-06-14 16:29:26'),
(63, 66, 2, 'What Is the Salary of a Data Scientist in Pune?', 'The average pay ranges from ₹ 7L to ₹17L annually. For freshers (0–1 year), it’s around ₹5L to ₹10L. Mostly, the salary varies based on experience. A good Data Science course can help you build the right skills and get better job opportunities in this field.', '2025-06-14 16:29:26', '2025-06-14 16:29:26'),
(64, 66, 2, 'What Are The Career Opportunities For Dаta Sciеnce Professionals?', 'There are enormous opportunities with multiple job roles available for data scientists after this Data Science Training in Pune. Some of the great roles you can apply for are: Data Scientist. Data Analyst, Data Engineer, Data Architect, Business Intelligence Analyst, Statistician, Machine Learning Engineer.', '2025-06-14 16:29:26', '2025-06-14 16:29:26'),
(65, 66, 2, 'What skills are needed for Data Science?', 'You have to be curious, analytical, and technical to become a Data Scientist. Some of the must-have skills you must know are Excel, Python, SQL, Data Visualisation tools, Machine Learning, and should have excellent communication skills. Digicrome teaches all of this practically from scratch in this Data Science course.', '2025-06-14 16:29:26', '2025-06-14 16:29:26'),
(66, 66, 2, 'What can I expect from a data scientist course in Pune?', 'You can expect quality learning with an all-round approach to teaching practically. The course must cover the key concepts and should be taught by expert trainers. Moreover, placement assistance to prepare you for the industry is a must.', '2025-06-14 16:29:26', '2025-06-14 16:29:26'),
(67, 66, 2, 'How is this Data Science Course changing the world?', 'Digicrome is among the best Data Science institutes in Pune. This course has changed the lives of more than 5k students, as they have easily transitioned to the field of Data Science. We teach from the foundations and strengthen your skills by providing exposure through internships and capstone projects incorporated in the curriculum.', '2025-06-14 16:29:26', '2025-06-14 16:29:26'),
(68, 63, 2, 'What is Data Science, and why is it important?', 'Data Science is the process of collecting, analyzing, and interpreting large amounts of data to find patterns and insights. It is important because it helps businesses solve problems, improve returns, and make better, data-based decisions for growth.', '2025-06-14 16:31:34', '2025-06-14 16:31:34'),
(69, 63, 2, 'Which industries are likely to hire Data Scientist Professionals?', 'Data Scientists are in demand across industries as firms depend on data-backed decisions more than ever today. Some of the top sectors hiring data professionals are: Healthcare, Finance, and Banking. Retail and E-Commerce, Telecommunications, Media and Entertainment, Government and Public Services, Manufacturing and Industrial Automation, and more.', '2025-06-14 16:31:34', '2025-06-14 16:31:34'),
(70, 63, 2, 'What Kind Of Salary Can I Expect As A Data Science Professional?', 'As you complete this Data Science Training Institute in Gurgaon, your salary on average will be around ₹26.6 lakhs per year. This can differ with experience, skills, and company. A fresher may start at an entry-level pay of ₹6.7 lakhs, and this over time and experience can go over ₹47.4 lakhs (top 10%).', '2025-06-14 16:31:34', '2025-06-14 16:31:34'),
(71, 63, 2, 'What are the Data Science job trends in Gurgaon?', 'Gurgaon has an increasing demand for Data Scientists, spread across industries. Specifically in technology, finance, healthcare, e-commerce, and consulting. Some of the important roles asked for more often in these industries are machine learning engineer, NLP specialist, and analytics consultant. The opportunities are not just for professionals but also for freshers.', '2025-06-14 16:31:34', '2025-06-14 16:31:34'),
(72, 63, 2, 'What skills will I gain from Digicrome’s Data Science training?', 'After this Data Science Course, you will learn all the foundational and core skills required in the field. You’ll gain hands-on experience with the latest tools and techniques like Python, Excel, SQL, EDA, Machine Learning, Tableau, Power BI, plus a capstone project and soft skills training.', '2025-06-14 16:31:34', '2025-06-14 16:31:34'),
(73, 63, 2, 'What are the fees for the Data Science course in Gurgaon?', 'This Data Science Course in Gurgaon by Digicrome is an 11-month online certfication program costing around ₹ 1,88,800 (including GST) covering from basic to advace level of Data science & AI in practice and not just theory, and the curriculum also includes a 12 Months Live Internship program along with 100% placement guarantee Aid*, mock interviews and soft skillls learning.', '2025-06-14 16:31:34', '2025-06-14 16:31:34'),
(74, 70, 2, 'Which Data Science Institute is best in Hyderabad?', 'Although many institutes offer data science training, Digicrome offers the best Data Science course in Hyderabad. We assure practical learning with live capstone projects, expert trainers, placement assistance, and an in-built internship in the curriculum to help build your portfolio.', '2025-06-14 16:32:00', '2025-06-14 16:32:00'),
(75, 70, 2, 'Is Data Science good for Beginners?', 'Yes, the Data Science Course can be taken up by a beginner. This course is structured in a way that even non-tech individuals can apply for it. So, if you are a curious person and interested in making sense of Data, you can learn here step by step from beginning to advanced.', '2025-06-14 16:32:00', '2025-06-14 16:32:00'),
(76, 70, 2, 'What is the average salary of a Data Scientist?', 'Hyderabad on average pays ₹14 L/Yr. While freshers can earn around ₹10L, with a minimum salary starting from ₹5L, this with experience can go up to ₹20L.', '2025-06-14 16:32:00', '2025-06-14 16:32:00'),
(77, 70, 2, 'Is there any job guarantee if I join this course?', 'We provide Job Guarantee Aid* to all our students applying for this course. We have partnered with over 500 hiring partners and have a dedicated team to help you get placed. Your Career Success is our top priority.', '2025-06-14 16:32:00', '2025-06-14 16:32:00'),
