(2, 1, 2, 'Predictive Customer Analytics for Retail', '<p>Build a machine learning model to predict customer purchase behavior and segment high-value customers. This project helps businesses improve retention and personalize marketing.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, Logistic Regression, Clustering, SQL, Tableau/Power BI</p>', '2025-06-07 12:03:52', '2025-06-07 12:03:52'),
(3, 1, 2, 'Real-Time Sales Dashboard Using Tableau & Power BI', '<p>Create a dynamic dashboard using Tableau and Power BI that visualizes key performance indicators for an e-commerce company, including profit trends, top-performing products, and customer demographics.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>Data Wrangling, Data Visualization, Tableau, Power BI, DAX, SQL</p>', '2025-06-07 12:04:45', '2025-06-07 12:04:45'),
(4, 1, 2, 'AI Resume Screening System', '<p>Develop an AI-powered system that screens resumes against job descriptions using NLP and recommends top candidates. Ideal for automating HR workflows.</p><p><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>Python, NLP (spaCy, NLTK), TF-IDF, Word Embeddings, Flask/Streamlit</p>', '2025-06-07 12:12:11', '2025-06-07 12:12:11'),
(5, 1, 2, 'Credit Risk Assessment Using Machine Learning', '<p>Build and train models that classify loan applicants as high or low risk based on historical financial data, using ensemble techniques and hyperparameter tuning.</p><p><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>Logistic Regression, Random Forest, XGBoost, GridSearchCV, Pandas, Scikit-learn</p>', '2025-06-07 12:12:53', '2025-06-07 12:12:53'),
(7, 1, 2, 'Stock Market Price Forecasting Using Time Series', '<p>Implement time series models to forecast stock prices and identify trends using historical financial datasets, incorporating statistical modeling and Python libraries.</p><p><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>ARIMA, Facebook Prophet, Python (Statsmodels, Pandas), Data Cleaning, Visualization</p>', '2025-06-07 15:10:42', '2025-06-07 15:10:42'),
(8, 1, 2, 'Deep Learning-Based Medical Image Classification', '<p>Train a CNN to classify X-ray or MRI images into diagnostic categories. This project demonstrates real-world applications of computer vision in healthcare.</p><p><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>TensorFlow/Keras, CNNs, Image Preprocessing, Data Augmentation, Transfer Learning</p>', '2025-06-07 15:11:25', '2025-06-07 15:11:25'),
(9, 1, 2, 'Conversational AI Chatbot with RAG and GPT', '<p>Develop a multi-purpose chatbot using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) with Transformer models to answer complex queries with context-aware responses.</p><p><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>Transformers (Hugging Face), GPT, Langchain, RAG, FastAPI, Vector Databases</p>', '2025-06-07 15:12:09', '2025-06-07 15:12:09'),
(10, 1, 2, 'Text Summarizer and Sentiment Analyzer for News Articles', '<p>Build an NLP pipeline to summarize news articles and classify their sentiment (positive, neutral, negative). Ideal for media monitoring or user review analysis.</p><p><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>BERT, Text Summarization, Sentiment Analysis, Transformers, Python</p>', '2025-06-07 15:12:45', '2025-06-07 15:12:45'),
(11, 1, 2, 'Generative AI for Image Creation Using GANs', '<p>Train a Generative Adversarial Network to create realistic images or artistic styles. Explore applications in marketing, content creation, and design.</p><p><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>TensorFlow, PyTorch, GANs (DCGAN, CycleGAN), Image Generation, CNNs</p>', '2025-06-07 15:13:16', '2025-06-07 15:13:16'),
(12, 61, 2, 'Financial Statement Analysis – Reliance Industries', '<p>In this project, students analyze five years of financial data from a leading diversified conglomerate to assess its overall financial health. They perform a detailed review of the income statement, balance sheet, and cash flow statement, calculate key ratios, and identify trends in profitability, solvency, liquidity, and operational efficiency. This helps build a foundation for valuation and modeling.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>&nbsp;Ratio analysis , Vertical &amp; horizontal analysis , DuPont decomposition , Free cash flow analysis</p>', '2025-06-07 16:43:40', '2025-06-07 16:43:40'),
(13, 61, 2, '-Statement Financial Model – Marico Ltd.', '<p>Learners build an integrated financial model projecting the income statement, balance sheet, and cash flow for a well-established consumer goods company. The model includes historical data analysis, forecasting revenue and expenses, modeling capital expenditures, working capital, and debt schedules. The goal is to create a fully linked model that adjusts automatically with assumption changes.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Skills Required:&nbsp;</strong><br>&nbsp;Excel-based modeling, Linking financial statements, Revenue and cost forecasting, Working capital modeling</p>', '2025-06-07 16:44:54', '2025-06-07 16:44:54'),
(14, 61, 2, 'Discounted Cash Flow (DCF) Valuation – Zomato', '<p>This project requires students to estimate the intrinsic value of a tech-driven business using the discounted cash flow approach. Learners forecast unlevered free cash flows, calculate the weighted average cost of capital, and determine terminal value using both Gordon Growth and Exit Multiple methods. The output is a full valuation report with sensitivity tables and scenario analysis.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Skills Required:&nbsp;</strong><br>Unlevered free cash flow projection, WACC estimation, &nbsp;Terminal value calculation, &nbsp;Valuation sensitivity analysis</p>', '2025-06-07 16:45:53', '2025-06-07 16:45:53'),
(15, 61, 2, 'Comparable Company Analysis – IT Services Sector', '<p>Students analyze a set of peer companies within the IT sector to derive relative valuation benchmarks. The project involves collecting financial metrics, adjusting for outliers or inconsistencies, and applying valuation multiples like EV/EBITDA and P/E to a target company. The output includes a comprehensive comps table and a justified valuation range.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Skills Required:&nbsp;</strong><br>&nbsp;Peer group screening, &nbsp;Financial normalization, &nbsp;Valuation multiples application, &nbsp;Comparable benchmarking</p>', '2025-06-07 16:46:44', '2025-06-07 16:46:44'),
(16, 61, 2, 'Precedent Transaction Analysis – FMCG M&A', '<p>In this case study, learners evaluate completed M&amp;A transactions in the FMCG industry. They gather transaction details, analyze deal structures, and derive valuation multiples from historical deals. The multiples are then applied to a hypothetical target company to assess acquisition pricing. Adjustments are made for non-recurring items and industry variations.&nbsp;<br><strong>Skills Required:&nbsp;</strong><br>&nbsp;Deal research and screening, &nbsp;Transaction multiple analysis, &nbsp;Adjusting financials for comparability, &nbsp;Building a precedent transaction table</p>', '2025-06-07 16:47:33', '2025-06-07 16:47:33'),
(17, 61, 2, 'LBO Modeling – Private Equity Buyout of Jubilant FoodWorks', '<p>This project simulates a private equity buyout of a well-known consumerfacing brand. Students structure an LBO model including sources and uses of funds, debt schedules, and exit scenarios. They analyze the returns to financial sponsors using IRR and MOIC metrics and test the impact of leverage under different operational outcomes.&nbsp;<br><strong>Skills Required:&nbsp;</strong><br>&nbsp;Debt and equity financing modeling, &nbsp;IRR and MOIC calculation, &nbsp;Cash sweep and repayment logic, &nbsp;Exit strategy sensitivity analysis</p>', '2025-06-07 16:48:37', '2025-06-07 16:48:37'),
(18, 61, 2, 'M&A Deal Modeling – HDFC Bank & HDFC Ltd. Merger', '<p>Students model a major all-stock merger between two large institutions. They calculate the combined entity’s pro forma earnings, estimate cost and revenue synergies, and assess the deal\'s accretion or dilution to shareholder value. The project concludes with risk scenarios, integration challenges, and impact on key financial metrics.&nbsp;<br><strong>Skills Required:&nbsp;</strong><br>&nbsp;Pro forma financial modeling, &nbsp;Synergy estimation, &nbsp;Accretion/dilution analysis, &nbsp;Purchase price allocation</p>', '2025-06-07 16:49:32', '2025-06-07 16:49:32'),
(19, 61, 2, 'Pitchbook Creation – IPO Pitch for Nykaa', '<p>Learners design a professional investment banking pitchbook for a highgrowth company planning to go public. The deck includes an executive summary, company overview, market opportunity analysis, financial highlights, and a valuation snapshot. Students focus on visual storytelling, formatting, and presenting data clearly to potential investors.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong><br>&nbsp;Company profiling and formatting, &nbsp;Capital markets research, &nbsp;Visual communication of financials, &nbsp;Structuring an IB-style pitchbook</p>', '2025-06-07 16:50:42', '2025-06-07 16:50:42'),
(20, 61, 2, 'Tableau Dashboard – Sector Comparison of Indian Banks', '<p>In this data visualization project, students create an interactive dashboard to compare financial performance across multiple banks. They present trends such as revenue growth, asset quality, ROE, and loan book composition using dynamic visual elements. The goal is to deliver actionable insights to stakeholders in a concise visual format.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Data structuring and transformation, &nbsp;KPI tracking and metric design, &nbsp;Building charts and dashboards, &nbsp;Financial storytelling with data</p>', '2025-06-07 16:51:39', '2025-06-07 16:51:39'),
(21, 61, 2, '. Python Automation Project – DCF Calculator', '<p>This project requires learners to build an automated business valuation tool using Python. The tool accepts assumptions like revenue growth, margins, and discount rate, and generates valuation outputs including enterprise value, equity value, and a valuation summary chart. Students practice coding logic and report generation.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Skills Required:</strong>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Python for finance (data handling, logic), Cash flow automation, Valuation formula integration, Visual output presentation</p>', '2025-06-07 16:52:55', '2025-06-07 16:52:55'),
