(43, 59, 2, '1. Retail Demand Forecasting System', '<p>Build a data-driven model to forecast product demand across different stores and regions for a retail chain. The system helps optimize inventory, reduce overstocking, and improve supply chain efficiency.<br><strong>Skills Required: </strong>Time Series Forecasting (ARIMA, Prophet), Python (Pandas, NumPy), Data Cleaning, Data Visualization (Matplotlib, Seaborn</p>', '2025-06-13 12:44:01', '2025-06-13 12:44:01'),
(44, 59, 2, 'Customer Segmentation for E-Commerce Platforms', '<p>Analyze user behavior and transaction data to segment customers based on purchasing patterns and demographics. This project helps companies build targeted marketing campaigns for each customer group.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Clustering (K-Means, Hierarchical), Data Preprocessing, PCA, Python, Matplotlib, Scikit-learn</p>', '2025-06-13 12:44:26', '2025-06-13 12:44:26'),
(45, 59, 2, 'Credit Card Fraud Detection System', '<p>Work with real transaction data to detect fraudulent activities using classification models. The project involves dealing with imbalanced datasets and real-time anomaly detection.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Classification Models (Logistic Regression, Random Forest), Imbalanced Data Handling (SMOTE), Python, ROC-AUC Metrics<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:44:51', '2025-06-13 12:44:51'),
(46, 59, 2, 'Netflix Data Analysis and Insights Dashboard', '<p>Analyze Netflix’s global content library to uncover trends in genres, release patterns, and viewer preferences. Present findings using interactive dashboards for business insights.<br><strong>Skills Required: </strong>Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), Data Cleaning, Python (Pandas, Seaborn), Dashboarding (Tableau or Power BI)<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:45:13', '2025-06-13 12:45:13'),
