(53, 3, 2, 'AI-based Stock Market News Summarizer & Analyzer', '<p>&nbsp;Scrape real-time financial news and use sentiment analysis to evaluate the impact on stock performance. Then, use Generative AI to convert raw data into clean, digestible investment insights, summaries, and risk alerts for traders.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Web Scraping (BeautifulSoup/Selenium), Sentiment Analysis, Text Summarization, LangChain, GPT APIs, Python<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:48:32', '2025-06-13 12:48:32'),
(54, 3, 2, 'Personalized Movie Recommendation System with Generative Reviews', '<p>&nbsp;Build a movie recommendation engine using collaborative filtering that not only suggests films based on user behavior but also generates custom reviews and movie summaries using LLMs to improve user engagement.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Recommendation Algorithms, Machine Learning, Matrix Factorization, Python, OpenAI API, Data Handling<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:48:53', '2025-06-13 12:48:53'),
(55, 3, 2, 'Fake News Detector with AI-Generated Explanations', '<p>Train a classification model to detect fake news articles from real ones, and use Generative AI to explain why a particular article was flagged, breaking down language patterns, sources, and credibility metrics.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> NLP, Supervised Learning, Scikit-learn, GPT-4 for Explanations, Tokenization, LangChain<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:49:14', '2025-06-13 12:49:14'),
(56, 3, 2, 'E-Commerce Product Image Caption Generator', '<p>Combine computer vision and GenAI to generate detailed product descriptions from images, helping e-commerce businesses automate their product listing processes. The AI understands product types, styles, and features from images and writes marketing-friendly captions.<br><strong>Skills Required: </strong>Deep Learning (CNNs), Vision-Language Models (BLIP, CLIP), Transformers, Image Preprocessing, Python</p>', '2025-06-13 12:49:33', '2025-06-13 12:49:33'),
(57, 3, 2, 'Smart City Traffic Flow Predictor with AI Reporting', '<p>&nbsp;Use IoT sensor data to analyze and predict peak traffic hours in metropolitan cities. The project integrates dashboards and uses GenAI to auto-generate policy recommendations, reducing congestion and improving route planning.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Time Series Analysis, Feature Engineering, Data Visualization (Plotly/Dash), GPT Reporting, Pandas<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:49:52', '2025-06-13 12:49:52'),
(58, 3, 2, 'Customer Churn Prediction with LLM-Generated Recommendations', '<p>&nbsp;Build a model that predicts which customers are most likely to leave a service or subscription. Then, use LLMs to generate actionable, segment-specific retention strategies such as discounts, loyalty points, or personalized messages.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Classification Models, Logistic Regression, Data Cleaning, GPT-4 Integration, Customer Analytics<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:50:19', '2025-06-13 12:50:19'),
(59, 3, 2, 'GenAI-Powered Legal Document Summarizer', '<p>&nbsp;Tackle the complexity of legal documents by developing a tool that extracts clauses, highlights key points, and summarizes entire contracts into human-readable formats—ideal for law firms, startups, and compliance teams.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Text Parsing, NLP, Transformers, LLM Summarization (LLM Chains), Domain-Specific Prompting, LangChain</p>', '2025-06-13 12:50:39', '2025-06-13 12:50:39'),
(60, 55, 2, 'Retail Demand Forecasting System', '<p>Build a data-driven model to forecast product demand across different stores and regions for a retail chain. The system helps optimize inventory, reduce overstocking, and improve supply chain efficiency.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Time Series Forecasting (ARIMA, Prophet), Python (Pandas, NumPy), Data Cleaning, Data Visualization (Matplotlib, Seaborn)</p>', '2025-06-13 12:51:35', '2025-06-13 12:51:35'),
(61, 55, 2, 'Customer Segmentation for E-Commerce Platforms', '<p>Analyze user behavior and transaction data to segment customers based on purchasing patterns and demographics. This project helps companies build targeted marketing campaigns for each customer group.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Clustering (K-Means, Hierarchical), Data Preprocessing, PCA, Python, Matplotlib, Scikit-learn<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:52:01', '2025-06-13 12:52:01'),
(62, 55, 2, 'Credit Card Fraud Detection System', '<p>Work with real transaction data to detect fraudulent activities using classification models. The project involves dealing with imbalanced datasets and real-time anomaly detection.<br><strong>Skills Required: </strong>Classification Models (Logistic Regression, Random Forest), Imbalanced Data Handling (SMOTE), Python, ROC-AUC Met</p>', '2025-06-13 12:52:29', '2025-06-13 12:52:29'),
(63, 55, 2, 'Netflix Data Analysis and Insights Dashboard', '<p>Analyze Netflix’s global content library to uncover trends in genres, release patterns, and viewer preferences. Present findings using interactive dashboards for business insights.<br><strong>Skills Required: </strong>Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), Data Cleaning, Python (Pandas, Seaborn), Dashboarding (Tableau or Power BI)<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:52:54', '2025-06-13 12:52:54'),
(64, 55, 2, 'Predicting Housing Prices with Machine Learning', '<p>Create a regression model that accurately predicts house prices based on features like location, size, and amenities. This is a classic supervised learning project with practical industry relevance.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Regression (Linear, Ridge, Lasso), Feature Engineering, Scikit-learn, Data Visualization, Hyperparameter Tuning</p>', '2025-06-13 12:53:14', '2025-06-13 12:53:14'),
(65, 55, 2, 'Employee Attrition Prediction for HR Teams', '<p>Help HR departments retain talent by predicting which employees are most likely to leave using historical employee data. This enables proactive retention strategies and workforce planning.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Classification, Exploratory Data Analysis, Logistic Regression, Feature Importance, Python<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-06-13 12:53:33', '2025-06-13 12:53:33'),
(66, 55, 2, 'Airbnb Market Analysis and Price Optimization', '<p>&nbsp;Analyze Airbnb listings to uncover pricing trends across cities and build a pricing recommendation engine based on property features and location demand.<br><strong>Skills Required:</strong> Data Cleaning, Regression Models, Geospatial Data Analysis, Python, Seaborn/Matplotlib, Feature Selection</p>', '2025-06-13 12:53:58', '2025-06-13 12:53:58');
